Emalunga eMkhandlu Wesive WaseWales akhatsateke ngekutsi atawubitwa ngekutsi bangema-muppet
Leti tizatfu tekutsi emalunga aleSigungu saVelonkhe akhatsateke, ngenca yekuhlelwa kwelibito lawo kutsi libe ngemaLunga ePhalamende yaseWales (Member of the Welsh Parliament, MWP).
Lomcondvo wavela ngenca yetinhlelo tekutsi lesigungu sibitwe ngekutsi yiPhalamende yaseWales.
Emalunga alowo mhlangano, laphuma kuto tonkhe tinhlangotsi tetembusave, akhatsateke ngekutsi angahle ahlekwe.
Lenye incenye yePhalamende yeLeburgu yakhombisa kukhatsateka ngelicembu layo, yatsi leligama lelisha livumelana nemavi esiWelsh twp kanye ne pwp.
Kubala labangasiwo emaWelsh, ligama lesiWelsh lelitsi twp lisho sitsi silima, kantsi leligama lelitsi pwp lisho kutsi "kuhlubuka".
Lenye yepolitiki ye Plaid Cymru itsi licembu layo 'alijabuli' ngalendzaba futsi yenta letinye tindlela tekusombulula lenkinga.
Lilunga le-Welsh Conservative Party latsi licembu lakhe likulungele kugucula ligama, kepha latsi ligama lelitsi MWP lifana kakhulu nelitsi muppet.
Kulendzaba, leligama lesiWelsh w lihunyushwa ngendlela lefanako naleligama lesi u ngesiNgisi sase Yorkshire.
Likomidi lelisebenta ngekhatsi kwalomhlangano, lelisebenta ngalomtsetfo lowenta kuguculwa kweligama, litsatse lesimo lesilandelayo:  Kuyacaca kutsi sincumo sekugcina mayelana neticu letitako temalunga alomhlangano sitawuba setandleni tawo.
UMtsetfo waHulumende waseWales wanga-2017 unikete Sigungu saVelonkhe saseWales lilungelo lekutsi sishintje ligama laso.
NgaJuni, lelikomidi latfumela imiphumela yekubonisana nemphakatsi ngalendzaba.
Ngetulu kwaloko, lelikomidi lasekela kutsi lelibito lemalunga aleliKhomishani lishintjwe libe ngu Lilunga lePhalamende yaseWales, nobe i-WMP ngesiNgisi, nanobe leligama lelitsi MWP belidvume kakhulu emphakatsini.
Emalunga aleSigungu ahle ahlela letinye tindlela tekusombulula tinkinga letivelako tekutfola sivumelwano, lokubuhlungu ku-Elin Jones, longumengameli waleSigungu, lotawetfula lomtsetfo etinhlelweni temnyaka letitawufika.
Lomtsetfo lowenta tingucuko utawuphindze uhlanganise naletinye tingucuko endleleni leMhlangano lesebentako ngayo, kufaka ekhatsi imitsetfo yekucitsa emalunga kanye nesakhiwo seluhlelo lwekomiti.
Emalunga eMkhandlu waVelonkhe atawukhona kuvota ngenchubomgomo yawo ngesikhatsi sekubekwa kwemtsetfo.
Bantfu baseMacedonia bavota kwentela kugucula ligama lelive
NgeLisontfo lelitako, bantfu batawukhetsa kutsi live labo litawuba yiRiphabhulikhi yaseNyakatfo yeMasedoniya nobe cha.
Lokuvota lokwentiwa nguwonkhewonkhe kutawusita ekucedzeni imphi lesekuphele emashumi eminyaka ihlangene neGrisi, lehlala endzaweni lebitwa ngekutsi yiMakedoniya.
Hulumende wase-Athene usolo utsi ligama lalelive lelisenyakatfo liyimibango, futsi uvamise kuphikisa emacebo ekufaka lelive ku-European Union nase NATO.
George Ivanov, umengameli waseMacedonia futsi longakatsandzi kutsi kube nencwadzi yekuhlola lechaza ligama lalelive, utsi angeke ayitsatse inhlonipho imiphumela yaloluhlolo.
Nanobe kunjalo, labo labatsandza lencwadzi, kufaka ekhatsi Ndvunankhulu Zoran Zaew, batsi lolushintjo luyadzingeka kute lelive likwati kujoyina i-European Union ne-NATO.
Tinkhulumo taseSt. Martin Church, eNew York, tivale ngenca yetinkinga temabandla aseHarlem
"Bantfu labadzala lengikhulume nabo batsi bekukhona indzawo yekudlela kanye nelibandla lapho bekunemakhona khona". kusho Michael Henry Adams.
"Kute lokulandzelako nyalo".
Njengobe asho, kuyintfo lecondzakalako kutsi emabha.
"Bantfu sebatihlanganisa ngetindlela letehlukene" waphawula.
 Emabha ayisekho indzawo yekuhlangana kwemalunga emphakatsi.
Ngalokwehlukile, akhatsatekile ngekutsi imali lephuma ekutsengisweni kwetintfo letisemakhayeni angeke ihlale sikhatsi lesidze njengobe bantfu labatsatsa tincumo bacabanga futsi 'ngemuva kwesikhatsi' batawube sebayakhona.
Wengeta watsi emasontfo angahle atsatfwe tindlu tekuhlala bantfu labangeke basekele emathempeli lalamanye.
Watsi: "Linyenti lebantfu labatsenga tindlu kuletakhiwo kutawuba bantfu labamhlophe, futsi loko kutawusheshisa kuvalwa kwetinkholo, ngobe bantfu labasha angeke babe ngemalunga aletikhungo".
Lamasontfo lamabili akhiwa libandla lebantfu labamhlophe ngaphambi kwekutsi Harlem ingene emphakatsini lomkhulu ngemnyaka wa 1870 (iSt Martin's Church yangena emphakatsini ngemuva kwemnyaka).
Libandla lelikhulu lemaWeseli labamhlophe lashiya lesigodzi ngemnyaka wa 1930.
Umhlangano webantfu labamnyama labaseMelika lowakhiwa endzaweni yakhona, watsatsa lilungelo lekuba ngumnikati walendlu.
Lisontfo le St. Martin's laphindze lahlulwa ngulesive lesiholwa ngu Rev. John Howard Johnson, lowahamba wayohlabela bantfu labatsengisa ngetitolo e125 Street (ligumbi lelikhulu le-Harlem) lebebangafuni kutsi bantfu labamnyama basebente nobe batfutfukiswe.
Umlilo wanga 1939 walimata lendlu kakhulu, nomakunjalo, emabandla aJohn Howard Johnson enta emasu ekwakha kabusha lithempeli futsi acoka kwakhiwa kwelicembu lemasango.
Umfundisi David Johnson, indvodzana yaJohn Howard Johnson kanye nendlalifa yakhe eSt Martin's Church, abebitwa ngekutigcabha ngekutsi ngu "Bell of the Poor".
Leso sati lesasicala kukhuluma nga-July, sachaza lamabhuku ngekutsi 'ligugu lemvelo' kanye 'nesitfunti semlandvo lesingenakuphikiswa'.
Tiffany Ng, losati selibhola letinsimbi eNyuvesi yaseMichigan, waphindze waphawula kutsi leliculo lekucala emhlabeni lelisetjentiswe ngumhlabeli lomnyama, lobekangumculi longu Dionisio A. Lind, lowatfutsela eRiverside Church eminyakeni lengu-18 leyendlulile, lapho bekamelele khona licembu lelikhulu.
Malcolm J. Merriweather watsi lisontfo laseSt. Martin alizange limtsatse sikhundla.
Etinyangeni letimbalwa letendlulile, kuSt Martin's Church, kwenteka tintfo letinyenti letiyinkimbinkimbi letibandzakanya bakhi netisebenti, letinye tato tibangelwe baholi benkholo, letinye tibangelwe liBandla le-Episcopal.
NgaJulayi, umtimba welibandla (umtimba lophetse lelive lonemalunga langasiwo emaKhristu) waveta kukhatsateka kwawo kulesikhungo, watsi "ufuna kutsi lelikhansela likhokhele lemali" kodvwa lelikhansela alizange lihlanganyele ekutsatseni bakhi kanye nebasebenti.
Labanye bantfu bakhonona ngekutsi kute kucaciseleka lokwentiwa yi-diocese.
