I-Sainsbury's ihlose kukhulisa umsebenti wayo emakethe yetintfo tekuhloba yase-UK
I-Sainsbury's ilahla titolo letifana neBoots, i-Superdrug ne-Debenhams, ngekwetfula ema-shop ayo lafaka ekhatsi tindzawo tekuhlobisa letitayela ema-shop kanye nebatsengisi labaceceshelwe.
Njengencenye yekutsengiswa lokukhulu kumakethe yetintfo tekuhloba yaseBrithani  lebita ema-£2.8 emabhiliyoni futsi lechubeka nekukhula nanobe kunekwehla kwetintfo tekuhloba letitfolakala etindzaweni letitsite  emashalofini lamakhulu etintfo tekuhloba atawuvela etitolo letingu-11 talelikhasimende. Uma lomklamo uphumelela, utawandziswa ngemnyaka lotako.
Kubuyela emuva kutekuhlobisa kubangelwa kufuna tindlela tekusebentisa indzawo lebeyitsatfwa ngemathelevishini, ngema-microwave kanye netintfo tasekhaya.
Ngekusho kwaSainsbury's, lelikhasimende litawuphindvwa kabili futsi litawukhipha tintfo letingu-3 000 letitfolakala ku-inthanethi, futsi kutawuba kwekucala kutsi kube nemikhicito levela kumikhicito lenjengemikhicito ye-Revlon, i-Essie, i-Tweeterman ne-Dr. PawPaw.
Tintfo letitsengiswako te-LOreal, Maybelline kanye ne-Burts Bees nato titawunikwa indzawo lenkhulu kanye netindzawo letitsite letifana naleti letitfolakala kuBoots.
Ngetulu kwaloko, lenkapani yetitolo letinkhulu ihlela kuvuselela umkhicito wayo wekugcobisa ema-boutique, kusukela nyalo, tintfo letinyenti titawuba ngete-vegan, lokuyintfo lefunwa kakhulu ngulabasha.
Ngetulu kwaloko, i-Fragrance Shop itawucala kusebentisa ema-test stalls lamabili e-Sainsbury's, lekuyindzawo yekucala levuleka e-Croydon leseNingizimu London, futsi lekulandzelako itawucala kusebenta eSelly Oak lese-Birmingham, ngasekupheleni kwemnyaka.
Kutfolakala kwetintfo tekutsengiswa ngetinkhundla tekutsengiswa kwetintfo nge-Internet kanye nekutsenga kudla lokuncane malanga onkhe etitolo tasendzaweni, kwenta kutsi timakethe letinkhulu tifune kutsi emakhasimende ato ete.
Mike Coupe, longumengameli weSainsbury's, utsi tindzawo tekutsengisa titawufana netitolo temakethe njengobe inethiwekhi yetitolo yetitolo yetama kulwa netitolo letitsengisa tintfo letishiyekako, letifana ne-Aldi ne-Lidl, ngekuniketa emasevisi lamanyenti kanye nemikhicito ngaphandle kwekudla.
Sainsbury's ifake ema-Argos stores emakhulwini etitolo, futsi isungula ema-Habitat stores lamaningi kusukela yatsenga letinkampani letimbili eminyakeni lemibili leyengcile, futsi itsi loku kwenta kutsi kukhicitwe kudla lokunyenti futsi kukhulise imali lekhokhwako.
Umzamo wekucala wekuhlela kabusha ema-cosmetics kanye nemitsi waphela ngemphumelelo.
Ekucaleni kwelikhulu lesi-21 leminyaka, iSainsbury's yasungula inkapani yekuhlanganyela neBoots, kepha kwaphela ngemuva kwekungevani mayelana nekwabiwa kwemali yetitolo letisebenta kumakhemisi lasetulu.
Sainsbury's isungula lisu lelisha ngemuva kwekutsengisa emakhemisi langu-281 kuCelesio, longumnikati we-Lloyds Pharmacy, ngemali lengemarandi langu-125 tigidzi temarandi eminyakeni lemitsatfu leyengcile.
I-Lloyds itakwandzisa luhlelo lwekwetfula imikhicito lemikhulu yetikhumba, kufaka ekhatsi iLa Roche-Posay neVichy, etitolo letine.
Paul Mills-Hicks, umcondzisi wetekutsengisa eSainsbury's, watsi: "Sishintjile indlela yekubukeka kanye neyekusebenta kwetindzawo tekuhlobisa kute sente bantfu babe nemphilo lencono.
Sitsenge imali ekucecesheni basebenti betfu kute basite batsengi ngesikhatsi batsenga.
Ema-brand etfu akwati kuhlangabetana nato tonkhe tidzingo, kantsi simo lesikahle kanye netindzawo letitsite kusenta sikwati kubamba emakhasimende lafuna tintfo telinongo, siphindze siphindze siphendvule indlela yekutsenga leyatiwako.
