I-tsunami kanye nekutamatama kwemhlaba e-Indonesia kwabhubhisa sihlenge, kwabulala bantfu labanyenti
Ngemuva kwekutamatama kwemhlaba esihlengeni saseLombok, tinhlangano letingekho ngaphasi kwahulumende tangaphandle tatjelwa kutsi asidzingi lusito.
Nanobe bantfu labangetulu kwa-10% baseLombok balahlekelwe tindlu tabo, tiphatsimandla atizange tichaze kutsi lesifo sibangelwe ngulesinye, lokuyintfo ledzingekile kute kuniketwe lusito lwemave emhlaba.
"Ngeshwa, etikhatsini letinyenti, tiphatsimandla tikwente kwacaca kutsi atifuni lusito lwemave emhlaba, ngako-ke simo sinzima", kusho Selina Sumbung.
Nanobe i-Save the Children ilungiselela kuya edolobheni lase-Indonesia iPalu, kute bufakazi bekutsi basebenti bemave emhlaba batawufika yini kulendzawo.
Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, sikhulumi se-ejensi yetehlakalo letisemhlabeni, watsi tiphatsimandla tase-Indonesia tihlatiya simo ePalu kute tibone kutsi ngabe lusito lolutfolakala ku-ejensi yemhlaba wonkhe kufanele yini luvumeleke.
Njengobe emave ase-Indonesia ahlaselwa tiphepho, lelive alikahlonyeliswa kutsi lingabhekana netimo letibuhlungu.
Nanobe tindzawo tekukhosela ema-tsunami takhiwe e-Aceh, kodvwa atikho etindzaweni letisemnceleni.
Kungabi khona kwe-siren ye-tsunami ePalu  nanobe bekunesecwayiso  kungenteka kutsi kwaba nemtselela ekubulaweni kwebantfu.
Ngisho nangesikhatsi sekuba nemoya lomuhle, kuhamba emkhatsini wetihlala-mkhatsi tase-Indonesia kungaba yinsayeya.
Tinhlekelele temvelo tenta kube matima kakhulu kusebenta.
Umkhumbi wesibhedlela losuka esichingini saseLombok uya edolobheni lasePalu, kepha kutawutsatsa emalanga lamatsatfu kutsi ufike.
