Nobe kunjalo, kutawubangela imvula lenkhulu etinyangeni letitako enyakatfo yeMexico kanye naseNingizimu-nshonalanga yeMelika.
Lesiphepho lesingu-Hurrican Rosa, lesinelizinga lelingemakhilomitha lalishumi nesikhombisa ngeli-awa, sabekwa kutsi sibe sigaba sekucala ngelihora lesihlanu ngeSontfo, ngesikhatsi siseningizimu-nshonalanga yePunta Eugenia, eMexico.
