Njengobe lesiphepho sicala kubakhona ePacific, siyacala kubakhona futsi siya ngasemphumalanga ye-United States, ngeMsombuluko, sihlasela eCalifornia Peninsula njengesichwaga, siletsa umoya lomunyeti losenyakatfo, usigudvulele eningizimu-nshonalanga ye-United States.
NgeMsombuluko, kutawuba netimvula letingaba ngemasentimitha langu-25 etindzaweni letinyenti taseMexico.
Emalangeni letako, umoya lomantana waseTropical, lohlangana nelizinga lelisetulu, utawubangela imvula lenkhulu eSouthwestern eMelika.
Kuletinye tindzawo, litulu lelingemasentimitha langu-2,5 kuya ku-10 litawubangela tikhukhula, kungcola kanye nekuguguleka kwetindzawo letisemahlane.
