Kubo bonkhe labo labatsintsekako, Kavanaugh watsi yena ucinisekile kutsi loko akuzange kwenteke.
Kungenteka kutsi bantfu lebebabukele ngaLesihlanu bebandlule ngisho naletingilosi letingu-20.4 million lebetishiwo yinkampani i-Nielsen.
Le-Company yabala linani lebantfu labamukela titeshi te-TV letingu-CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel kanye ne-MSNBC.
Nanobe kunjalo, lamanye ema-stations, kufaka ekhatsi i-PBS, i-C-SPAN ne-Fox Business Network, bekungakabi netinombolo letatikhona.
Ngetulu kwaloko, iNielsen ivame kuba nenkinga yekukala kubukwa kwebantfu emsebentini.
Loku kufana nekubuka imidlalo ye-baseball nobe umklomelo we-American Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences.
Ngekusho kwe-Nielsen, i-Fox News Channel, lebeyinetindzaba letinyenti letakhombisa kutsi Kavanaugh sewukhetsiwe, yaba nebantfu labakhulu, lebebabukela bantfu labangu-5.69 000 ngesikhatsi selusuku lonkhe.
I-ABC inebantfu labangu 3.26 million, futsi ingumlandvo.
