Imibono leyehlukene ngekuvakasha kwa-Erdogan e-Cologne
Ngesikhatsi baholi baseTurkey nebaseJalimane bajabulela kudla kwasekuseni ngeMgcibelo (ngoSeptember 29) eBerlin, bebajabulile futsi banemusa.
Bekulilanga lekugcina lekuvakasha kwaMengameli Erdogan eJalimane, lokuyintfo lebeyitsintsa kakhulu, lebeyihlose kutfutfukisa budlelwane emkhatsini walabangani bakhe be-NATO.
Loku kwaholela ekutseni kube netimphi etindzabeni letifaka ekhatsi emalungelo eluntfu, inkhululeko yebetindzaba kanye nekujoyina kweTurkey ku-European Union.
Ngemuva kwalomhlangano, Erdogan waya eColonia, lapho avula khona lisontfo lelikhulu.
Lelidolobha linelinani lelikhulu lebantfu baseTurkey labahlala ngaphandle kwelive labo.
Emaphoyisa atsi ngenca yetizatfu tekuphepha, bantfu labangu-25 000 bebabhace embikwelithempeli, kodvwa basekeli baMengameli babutsana endzaweni lephakeme kute babone umholi wabo.
Emakhulu ebantfu labamelene na-Erdogan - lokufaka ekhatsi emaKurd lamanyenti - nabo bakhetse kuveta imibono yabo, balahla inchubomgomo yemholi waseTurkey kanye nesincumo sahulumende waseJalimane sekwenta imitsetfo kulelive.
Imibhikisho lephikisanako ikhombisa kwehlukana lokubangelwe kuvakasha kwaLushawulo, lobitwa ngekutsi yindvodza lephumelelako kuletinye tive taseTurkey letihlala eGermany, kantsi labanye batsi ungumuntfu lonemandla.
