Emaphoyisa labekhona abenelihlazo lelimfishane ebusweni.
Umkhulumeli walenkantolo watsi: "Ekhikhini lekujeziswa e-HMP Long Lartin, basebenti labaceceshwe ngalokukhetsekile bebabandzakanyeka kuloluhlelo.
Emaphoyisa lasitfupha alimala kancane.
