NgaJuni, umbiko waveta kutsi umcondzisi walenkantolo kwadzingeka kutsi aye esibhedlela ngemuva kwekuhlaselwa ngulomunye webantfu labebaseluvalelweni.
Nga-October, emaphoyisa abitwa kulelihhovisi ngenca yetingoti letatenteka ngesikhatsi tisebenti tihlaselwa ngemabhola ekudlala ibhiliyadi.
Kufika kwetikhukhula letibangelwa nguSiphepho Rosa, kubeka iPhoenix, Las Vegas neSalt Lake City engotini (lokungaba nemtselela lomuhle etindzaweni letinesomiso)
Kuvamile kutsi kube nekucindzeteleka lokukhulu lokwenteka e-Arizona, futsi kungenteka kutsi kwenteke ekucaleni kweliviki lelitako.
I-National Weather Service seyivele ikhiphe secwayiso sekuba netikhukhula ngeMsombuluko nangoLesibili eWestern Arizona, Southern Nevada, Southern California, kanye nase Utah, kufaka ekhatsi emadolobha lafana nePhoenix, Flagstaff, Las Vegas kanye neSalt Lake City.
Kulindzeleke kutsi iRosa itawugeleta ngeLesibili idzabule iPhoenix bese kutsi ngeMsombuluko ntambama, kucale imvula lenkhulu.
I-National Weather Service yasePhoenix yatise nge-Twitter kutsi kusukela nga-1950 sekube netinhlekelele tetinhlekelele letingu-10 letitibambe tibe nguletisemkhatsini wetinhlekelele letinkhulu nobe letingaphansi kwetimo letinemandla letisendzaweni lengemakhilomitha langu-320 kusuka ePhoenix.
Sichwaga Katrina (nga-1967) besisondzela emakhilomitha langu-40 kusuka esifundzeni sase-Arizona.
I-National Hurricane Center ibike kutsi kutawuba nemvula lenkhulu lengemamitha lalishumi kuya kulasihlanu, futsi kuletinye tindzawo taseMogollon Rim, e-Arizona, kungaba nemvula lenkhulu lengemamitha lalishumi nesihlanu.
Letinye tindzawo letisemahlane eNingizimu-nshonalanga  kufaka ekhatsi iRocky Mountains lesemkhatsini kanye neGreat Basin  litulu lemanti litokhokha emkhatsini wa 2.5 kuya ku 5 cm, kantsi kuletinye tindzawo litokhokha kufika ku 10 cm.
Bantfu labangekho etindzaweni letinesehlakalo lesibuhlungu semvula, bangabese bayabusiswa nguletimvula letihambisana neSiphepho Rosa, njengobe lesifundza sesinesikhatsi lesidze sinesomiso.
Nanobe tikhukhula tiyingoti, lokunye kwaloku kutawulungisa simo eNingizimu-nshonalanga, lapho kunesomiso khona.
I-U.S. Drought Monitor ibika kutsi cishe emaphesenti langu-40 e-Arizona ahlaselwa ngumkhuhlane wesomiso lesibi kakhulu, njengobe kubikwa ku-weather.com.
Sichwaga Rosa sitawucala sifike eCalifornia Peninsula eMexico.
NgeLisontfo ekuseni, lesiphepho lesinguRosa besisolo sihamba ngemandla aso, futsi besibengesikhatsi sihamba ngesivinini lesingu-137 km/h. Nyalo sesikadze singemakhilomitha langu-620 eningizimu yePunta Eugenia eMexico, futsi sihamba ngesivinini lesingu-19 km/h sisenyakatfo.
Lesiphepho sihlangana nemanti labandzako ase Pacific, lokwenta kutsi sibe butsakatsaka.
Sibike kutsi lesichwaga sitawufika eMexico ngeLisontfo ntsambama nobe kusihlwa.
Kujula kwemvula etindzaweni letitsite eMexico kungabangela tikhukhula.
I-weather.com ibika kutsi kusuka eCalifornia Peninsula kuya enyakatfo-nshonalanga ye Sonora, litulu litawubanjwa ngemasentimitha langu-7 kuya ku-15 kepha lingafika ku-25 cm.
Ngemuva kwaloko, lesiphepho lesingu-Rosa sitawuhamba ngesheya kweMexico sibe siphepho lesivutsa kakhulu, bese sifika esifundzeni sase-Arizona ekuseni kakhulu ngaLesibili, sibe siphepho lesivutsa kakhulu, bese sifika eningizimu ye-Utah ngaLesibili kusihlwa.
"Lusongo lolukhulu lweSiphepho Rosa nobe lokunye lokusele kuso, lutawubangela imvula lenkhulu eCalifornia Peninsula, enyakatfo-nshonalanga ye-Sonora kanye nasehlane leliseningizimu-nshonalanga ye-United States", kusho i-National Hurricane Center.
Kutawubakhona imvula lenkhulu letawubangela tikhukhula letiyingoti, titfunti letinyakatako letitawufikela ehlane kanye netigodzi letinetigodzi letinkhulu letitawufikela etintsabeni.
