Bantfu Labakhulu Bahlushwa Kuhlaselwa Kwemhlaba Kanye Ne-tsunami E-Indonesia
NgeMgcibelo, tiphatsimandla tatsi bantfu labangu-384 bafile - labanyenti babo batfunjwa ngemagagasi lamakhulu labetibhubhisa emabhishi - ngemuva kwekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kanye ne-tsunami e-Indonesia, esichingini saseSulawesi.
NgeLesihlanu, emakhulu ebantfu ahlangana elugwini ePalu kute bahlanganyele kulomkhosi, futsi nasekuhlwa, emagagasi labengaba ngemamitha langu-20 budze, ahamba atsatsa bantfu labanyenti futsi abhubhisa konkhe lokwakusendleleni yawo.
Le-tsunami yabangelwa kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwafinyelela ku-7.5.
"Ngesikhatsi kuvela ingoti, bantfu lebebaselugwini abazange basuke ngekushesha futsi babulawa ngu-tsunami", kusho Sutopo Purwo Nugroho, lokhulumela i-BNPD, e-Indonesia, emhlanganweni we-tsunami eJakarta.
"Leti tsunami betihlasela konkhe lokukuyo, titsatsa timoto, tingodvo kanye netindlu", kusho Nugroho.
Watsi labanye bantfu basindza ngekukhuphukela etihlahleni.
Bantfu labangu-16,700 basusiwe bayiswa etindzaweni letingu-24 ePalu.
Titfombe letivela emoyeni letishicilelwe yi-NCA, tikhombisa tindlu letinyenti kanye netitolo letishayekile, emabhuloho labhujisiwe kanye nemasontfo labhajwe ngemanti.
NgaMgcibelo, kuvele kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu edolobheni leliselwandle.
Kube netinhlekelele temhlaba letinkhulu kakhulu endzaweni lenebantfu labangaba tigidzi letingu-2.4.
Ngekusho kwe-Indonesian Agency for Technology Assessment and Use (BPPT), emandla lakhululwa ngulesihlakalo lesatenteka ngaLesihlanu, abengacishe abe ngemahlandla langemakhulu lamabili emandla lebekaphephwe ngebhomu le-athomu lelahlaselwa eHiroshima eMphini Yelive Yesibili.
Lesitatimende satsi lendzawo lehlala khona lelidolobha, lelisekugcineni kweligede lelidze, lingaba nemtselela lomkhulu ku-tsunami.
Sutopo Purwo Nugroho wachaza lomonakalo ngekutsi "ngulobukhulu" watsi tindlu letinyenti, tibhedlela, tindzawo tekutsengisela kanye nemahhotela kwabhidlika.
Watsi labanye bantfu batfolwe ngaphansi kwetakhiwo letatibhidlikile, bantfu labangu-540 balimala, kantsi labanye labangu-29 basengakabonakali kutsi basaphila yini.
Nugroho watsi kufa kanye nekulimala kungenteka kube kukhulu elugwini lolungemakhilomitha langu-300 enyakatfo yePalu, endzaweni lebitwa ngekutsi yiDonggala, lebeyisedvute nendzawo yekuhlaselwa.
Ngekusho kwaNugroho, tindlela tekuchumana "tishaywe yimphumelelo" ngako-ke kute lokwatiko lokutfolakalako esifundzeni sase Donggala.
"Kulapho kuhlala khona bantfu labangetulu kwa-300 000", kusho incwadzi ye-Red Cross, lebuye yatsi tisebenti netisebenti tetinhlangano tiya etindzaweni letitsintsekile.
"Singahle sikhulume ngenhlekelele nyalo, nanobe simo singase sibe sibi kakhulu", kusho sitatimende.
NgaMgcibelo, lelihhovisi le-NCS lahlangabetana nekugceka lokukhulu ngenca yekungakhoni kutfola lwati mayelana ne-tsunami lehlele ePalu, kodvwa tiphatsimandla tatsi lamagagasi efika ngemuva kwekuba sekukhishwe secwayiso.
Kulenye yetindzaba tekuchumana, umbhali wemlandvo utsi indvodza letsite imemeta isesakhiweni setakhiwo setindlu, itjela bantfu kutsi kutawugcwala tsunami.
Ngemizuzu lembalwa, lolubondza lwemanti lwabhidlika, kwahosha takhiwo netimoto.
