I-United States kufanele iphindze kabili imali yayo yekucwaninga nge-AI
Umtsengisi kanye nemphenyi lowati nge-AI lokutsiwa nguKai-Fu Lee, losebenta ku-Google, Microsoft kanye ne-Apple, utsi njengobe i-China ikhula kulomkhakha, i-United States ingadzinga kukhulisa imali yayo ekucwaningeni nge-AI.
Lesiphakamiso sihlobene netimemetelo letiphuma kuhulumende waseMelika mayelana nebuhlakani lobentiwe (i-AI), nanobe i-USA ingenayo indlela leyetayelekile yekusebentisa i-AI.
Kantsi futsi, umnyaka lowengcile, iChina yetfula luhlelo lwayo lwekutsi nga 2030 ibe live lelisungula kakhulu kubuhlakani lobentiwe.
"Kufanele sicale ngekuphindzaphindza imali yekucwaninga nge-AI: onkhe lamanye emave aseceleni kwe-United States, futsi setama kwenta lokunye lokusha kuloluhlelo", kusho Kai-Fu Lee.
Kulombiko wakhe ku CNBC, waphindze watsi kucinisa imali lengetiwe kungenta kutsi kube nelitfuba lelikhulu lekutsi kube nekuhlakanipha lokwentiwa bantfu eMelika.
Lee, lowabhala incwadzi letsi AI Superpowers: China, Silicon Valley and the New World Order (Inhlangano yebuhlakani lobusebenta ngekusebentisa i-AI: iChina, iSilicon Valley kanye neLuhlelo Lwelwati Lusha) leyashicilelwa ngenyanga le, ngu-Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, longumengameli we Sinovation Ventures.
Ngabo-1980, Kai-Fu Lee wasebenta eCarnegie Mellon University, asebenta ekwakheni indlela ye-AI leyaphumelela ku-Othello, umdlali we-Othello waseMelika, wase uba ngumholi we-Microsoft Research, waba ngumengameli we-Google lese-China.
Lee wavuma kutsi tindlela letisetjentiswako tahulumende waseMelika tiphumelele, njengemncintiswano we-Defense Advanced Research Projects Agency (DARPA) wekuhlela ema robot lamasha, waphindze wabuta kutsi kutawuphindze kwenteke nini lomncintiswano, ngobe utsi utawusita ekutsatseni bantfu labatawufuna kubona tintfo ngendlela leyehlukile.
Njengobe Kai-Fu Lee asho, bososayensi eMelika bavame kusebenta kamatima kute batfole imali yekusekela hulumende.
"Akusibo bantfu baseChina labasusa bafundzi betfu labakhulu, kodvwa tinkapani", kusho Lee.
Eminyakeni lembalwa leyengcile, i-Facebook, i-Google naletinye tinkampani te-tech besebaticeceshe bososayensi labadvumile kutsi basebente ku-AI.
Ngekwembono waLee, kugucula inchubomgomo yekungena eveni kungasita iMelika ekutfutfukiseni i-AI.
"Ngicabanga kutsi bantfu labati umsebenti wabo wekusebentisa i-AI, labane-PhD, kufanele baniketwe likhadi lelimhlophe", washo.
NgaJulayi 2017, Umkhandlu Wesive waseChina wakhipha luhlelo lwekwakha butekucamba besitukulwane lesilandzelako.
Njengobe Lee asho, iNational Natural Science Foundation yase China iniketa imali kumalunga etikhungo tetemfundvo ngendlela lefana ne-US National Science Foundation kanye naletinye tinhlangano tahulumende letiniketa imali kutesayensi baseMelika.
Ekucaleni kwalomnyaka, liTiko Letekuvikela laseMelika lavula sikhungo lesihlangene sekuhlakanipha kwebuhlakani (Joint Artificial Intelligence Center) lesitawufaka ekhatsi emabhizinisi kanye netesayensi, kantsi neNdlu Lemhlophe yamemetela kutsi kutawubekwa liKomiti lelikhetsekile lebuhlakani lobentiwe ngebuhlakani.
Kulenyanga, i-DARPA yatsi itawuniketa tigidzigidzi letimbili temarandi embonini yetintfo letibita ngekutsi yi-AI Next.
I-National Science Foundation nyalo seyifaka imali lengetulu kwetigidzigidzi letilikhulu temadola ngemnyaka ekucwaningeni nge-AI.
Ngesikhatsi lesifanako, umkhankhaso waseMelika wekwakha likomidi leliphakeme lekuvikela lizinga lebuhlakani lobentiwe ngetintfo letisetjentiswako awukenteki tinyanga letinyenti.
