Sitatimende semhlangano weLebalers' Party Nottingham East satsi: "Sifuna kutsi imihlangano yetfu ibe yimininingwane futsi ikhiphe titselo".
Eminyakeni lesiphohlongo lengiyicitse ngiyilunga le-Labor, loku bekungumkhuba lobekuba khona emihlanganweni ye-General Committee lechubekako ngaLesihlanu ntsambama.
Lokubuhlungu kutsi, lamuhla, imihlangano leminyenti ayenti njalo.
Kuyacaca kutsi licembu lebasebenti alivumi kutsi kube nemibono leyehlukene, futsi yonkhe imibono iyahlolwa kutsi iyahambisana yini nebaholi belicembu.
Konkhe kwacala ngemuva kwekutsi Jeremy Corbyn abe ngumengameli, futsi labanye bangani bami lebengibona kutsi banembono lofanako, bacabanga kutsi ngitawugucula indlela lengiphila ngayo, ngitsatse tincumo lebengingavumelani nato, ngetindzaba letifana nekuvikeleka kwavelonkhe kanye nemakethe lefanako ye-EU.
Ngemuva kwekukhuluma kwami emphakatsini, noma ngabe ngitsini, ngivame kuhlangabetana nekuhlaselwa ku-social media, ngitsi akukafaneli ngibe ngulomuntfu, ngitsi angiyekele kuba yincenye yelicembu le-Labor.
Loku akuyona nje intfo lengiyentile.
Nginenhlanhla lenkhulu kunebangani bami ngobe imibono lengiyitfolako isuke iyembusave.
Ngiyawujabulela umsebenti wabo kanye nekucinisela kwalabo labasebenta nabo lababhekana nekuhlukunyetwa ngekwebulili nobe ngebuhlanga onkhe malanga, kodvwa bangete bakugwema kuchubeka nekwenta loko.
Lokunye lokudvumata kakhulu mayelana netembusave nyalo kutsi sekuyintfo levamile kutsi bantfu bahlaze labanye.
Viki leliphelile Jeremy Corbyn watsi iLabour Party kufanele isekele lisiko lekutsetselela.
Empeleni, asisesiyo inhlangano yebantfu labanemibono leyehlukene, futsi ngekuphakanyiswa kwevoti yekungetsembeki kanye nekuguculwa kwetimiso tekukhetsa, umbono welicembu uyacitseka.
Kuleminyaka lemibili leyengcile, ngelulekwe kanyenti kutsi ngingatigodli futsi ngingatisho tintfo letitsite, bese konkhe kuyolunga.
Kodvwa loko akuzange kungente ngibe yincenye yepolitiki.
Kusukela ngajoyina i-Labour Party eminyakeni lengu-32 leyengcile ngesikhatsi ngisesemncane ngenca yekunganakwa kwahulumende wa Margaret Thatcher lokwaholela ekutseni likilasi lami lelisesikolweni libhidlike, bengisolo ngenta konkhe lokusemandleni ami kute ngente ncono lizinga letinsita temphakatsi kubantfu labaswele  njengalomunye welikhansela lelidolobha kanye nanjengeNdvuna yeMbuso.
Angizange ngivume kutsi ngitifihla loko lengikukholelwako, ngisho nangesikhatsi selukhetfo lwami lwekugcina.
Bonkhe bantfu baseNottingham East bebakwati loko lebengikwenta futsi bebati nekungavumelani kwami nebaholi belicembu.
Kulabo labasekela lomtsetfo welusuku lwekutalwa kwebantfu, ngitsandza kutjela labantfu kutsi angiyicondzi indlela labafuna kulahlekelwa sikhatsi nemandla abo ngekubhekana nekwetsembeka kwami kuloluphawu lwe-Laborist lobukene ne-Brexit letako, letawulimata emakhaya, emabhizinisi kanye netinsita temphakatsi.
Kodvwa umlayeto wami lobaluleke kakhulu, hhayi ku-Nottingham Momentum, kepha kulabo labangivukelako (emaLeber kanye nalabanye), utsi: Ngiyatigcabha ngekukhonta, futsi ngetsembisa kutsi kute lokusongelako kutsi ngitawuyekela, futsi kute netinhloso tepolitiki letisengakefiki letitawuvele tingicedze emandla ekwenta loko lengikukholelwako, futsi ngikwente kube yintsandvo yenu nonkhe.
