Njengobe iBolivia ingena elwandle, kukhumbula lolugede lwalo lolwalahlwa yiChile kulemphi yeminyaka yabo-1800 lebeyitsintsa imitfombo yemanti, kusolo kusemkhatsini wekuphupha ngekuhamba kweLwandle iPacific futsi.
