John Edward: Emakhono elulwimi ladzingekile kubantfu bemhlaba
Tikolwa letitimele eScotland tijabulela kakhulu kutfola tifundvo letitsite  nga-2018 tibe nemiphumela lemihle kakhulu etihlolweni, kanye nemphumelelo lecinisekisiwe kutemidlalo, tebuciko, temculo kanye naleminye imisebenti lehlanganyelwe.
Tikolwa letimelelwa yi Scottish Council of Independent Schools (SCIS), letinemalunga langetulu kwa-30 000 eScotland, tifuna kuniketa bafundzi nebatali babo lizinga lelihle kakhulu lekusebenta.
Tikolwa letitimele tihlose kucecesha bafundzi kutsi bachubele embili emfundvo lephakeme, bakhetse umsebenti lotawubaholela emisebentini yabo, futsi bakwati kuchaza indzima yabo njengebahlali bemhlaba.
Njengemboni yemfundvo lekhona kwakha nekusebentisa luhlelo lwekuhlela tifundvo letitsite, sibona kutsi tilwimi tesimanje tihlala tiluhlobo lolutsandvwa kakhulu lwetifundvo letitsite.
Nelson Mandela watsi: "Nawukhuluma nemuntfu ngelulwimi lalucondzako, loko kuyamtsintsa.
Nangabe ukhuluma naye ngelulwimi lwakhe, loko kuyamtsintsa inhlitiyo.
Loku kusikhumbuta ngalokucacile kutsi singete sasitsembela elulwimini lwesiNgisi kuphela uma sifuna kwakha budlelwane nekwetsembana nebantfu bakulamanye emave.
Imiphumela yaloluhlolo loluphelile kulomnyaka ikhombisa kutsi tilwimi tibekwe embili kuloluhlu, kantsi tikolwa letitimele ngito letinelizinga lelisetulu lekuphumelela.
Bonkhe bafundzi labangu-68% labafundza lolunye lulwimi batfola emamaki laphakeme kunalawa.
Imininingwane lebutfwe etikolweni letingu-74 letinge-SCIS ikhombise kutsi bafundzi labangemaphesenti langu-72 batfole emamaki la-A esiMandarin, kantsi emaphesenti langu-72 ebantfu labafundza siJalimane, emaphesenti langu-69 ebantfu labafundza siFulentshi, kanye nemaphesenti langu-63 ebantfu labafundza siSpanish nabo batfole emamaki la-A.
Loku kukhombisa kutsi tikolwa letitimele eScotland tikhutsata lulwimi lwangaphandle njengelulwimi loludzingekako lolutawusetjentiswa bantfwana kanye nebantfu labasha esikhatsini lesitako.
Lamuhla, kufundziswa kwetilwimi njengetifundvo letikhetsiwe, kufundziswa ngendlela lefanako naleyo yekufundziswa kwetihloko te-STEM (Science, Technology, Engineering and Mathematics) etikolweni letitimele nakuletinye tindzawo.
Luhlolo lwanga-2014 lolwentiwe liKhomishani lase-UK leTemisebenti nemaKhono, lwaveta kutsi kuba matima kwebasebenti kutfola tikhala temisebenti, kumaphesenti langu-17 kwehluleka kwemakhono elulwimi.
Kungako-ke emakhono elulwimi ayintfo lebalulekile yekulungiselela bantfu labasha kutsi bacale umsebenti.
Leti tifundvo tibalulekile emhlabeni lohlanganisiwe, lapho khona kunemisebenti leminyenti ledzinga lwati lwetilwimi.
Emakhono laphilako, lafana nekufundza lulwimi lwesibili, atawuniketa inzuzo lenkhulu esikhatsini lesitako  nobe ngabe ukhetse luhlobo lolunjani lwekukhula ngemakhono.
Kukwati kukhuluma nebantfu bakulamanye emave ngalokucondzile kwenta umuntfu lofundza tilwimi letinyenti abe nelikhono lelikhulu kunalomncintiswano.
Ngekusho kweluphenyo lwe-YouGov lwanga-2013, lolwahlanganiswa nebantfu labadzala labangetulu kwa-4000 base-UK, 75% wabo bebangakwati kukhuluma lulwimi lolwengetiwe kahle ngalokwenele kutsi bakwati kuchumana nalabanye, kantsi siFulentji bekusilo lulwimi lolunetinombolo letimbili kuphela, lokungu-15%.
Kungako-ke kubalulekile kutsi bantfwana bafundze tilwimi letinsha.
Kumunya tilwimi letinyenti, ikakhulukati kuletinye taleto tilwimi letisemnotfweni lotfutfukako, kutawenta bantfwana bakwati kutfola umsebenti lofanele.
KuScotland, tikolwa titawehluka ngetilwimi letifundziswa tona.
Tikolwa letinyenti titawucala kufundzisa ngetilwimi letisembili, kantsi letinye titawufundzisa ngetilwimi letibaluleke kakhulu eBrithani nga-2020, njengesiMandarin noma siJapane.
Nobe ngabe ngutiphi tintfo umntfwana latifunako, etikolweni letitimele kutawuba neluhlu lwetilwimi, letifundziswa bacashi labanelikhono.
Tikolwa te-Independent eScotland tinemtfwalo wekwakha indzawo yekufundza letawulungiselela bantfwana futsi ibaphe emakhono labadzingako kute baphumelele  nobe ngabe likusasa libaphatseleni.
Lamuhla, kute longakuphika kutsi etindzaweni temabhizinisi emhlaba wonkhe tilwimi tisasebenta njengentfo lebalulekile ngelikusasa lelive, futsi loko kumele kubonakale emfundvweni.
Tilwimi tesimanje kumele titsatfwe ngekutsi 'tikwati kukhulumisana nemave ngemave'.
Tikolwa letitimele titawuchubeka tinikete bantfu labasha baseScotland kukhetsa lokunyenti, kuhlukahlukana kanye nemazinga.
Kumane nje kufanele kube njalo.
John Edward, umengameli we Scottish Council of Independent Schools
