Luke Walton, umceceshi wema-Lakers, umemetele kutsi LeBron James utawudlala umdlalo we-pre-season ngeSontfo, utawudlala ne-Denver Nuggets eSan Diego.
Asati kutsi utawudlala imizuzu lemingaki.
"Ngetulu kwalokunye, kepha ngaphansi kwa-48", kusho Walton ku-website ye-Lakers.
Mike Trudell, umbhali we-Lakers, watfumela umlayeto ku-Twitter watsi James utawudlala imizuzu lembalwa.
Ngemuva kwekuceceshwa kwekucala kweliviki, James wabutwa ngemalungiselelo akhe emidlalo lesitfupha ye-Lakers.
"Ngekuya kwesikhatsi lengikuso, angidzingi kutsi ngichubeke nemidlalo yasesikhatsini sekucala kute ngilungele lomdlalo", kwasho yena.
Ngako-ke, kukhetsa kwaTrump eWest Virginia, siteshi se-YouTube
Mengameli Donald Trump utawucala umhlangano wekukhetsa bantfu eWheeling, eWest Virginia, lamuhla kusihlwa.
Loku kwekucala kwemihlangano lesihlanu lehlelwe nguTrump kutsi ibe khona evikini lelitako, kanye nekumiswa kwetindzawo letiyinsika kuye, letifaka ekhatsi iTennessee neMississippi.
Njengobe sekunemvumo yekubanjwa kwesikhundla sakhe lesisemtsetfweni eNkantolo lePhakeme, Trump ufuna kwakha kwesekela elukhetfweni lolutako, ngobe emaRiphabhulikhi angahle alahlekelwe kulawula kweCongress ngesikhatsi sekubanjwa kwevoti ngaNovemba.
Ngusiphi sikhatsi lesitawuba khona umhlangano waTrump eWest Virginia lamuhla ntsambama, futsi utawubukelwa kuphi ku-Internet?
Ngako-ke, umcimbi wekukhetsa Trump e Wheeling, eWest Virginia, utawubanjwa nga-19:00 kusihlwa lamuhla, ngaMgcibelo, September 29, 2018.
Ngako-ke, umcimbi waTrump eWest Virginia utawulandzelwa ngekubhala live ku-YouTube.
Trump utawukhuluma ngetinkhulumo talokungenani ngeliviki letiphatselene nekubekwa kwaBret Kavanaugh kutsi abe ngumengameli weNkantolo lePhakeme, lokube yintfo lematima ngenca yetinsolo tekutiphatsa kabi ngekwelicansi, kanye nevoti lebekumele ilandzelwe yi-Senate kutsi imise lukhetfo lwa-Mengameli liviki linye, ngesikhatsi kuphenywa licala le-FBI.
Kodvwa-ke, inhloso lenkhulu yaloluhlelo lwekukhetsa kutsi kube khona ema-Rephabliki lafuna kusekela lukhetfo lolumatima lwanga-Novemba.
Ngako-ke, umkhankaso waMengameli Trump wekubamba imihlangano lesihlanu ngeliviki lelitako uhlose kuhlanganisa emavolontiya kanye nebasekeli kute basite emaRiphabliki ekuvikeleni kanye nekukhulisa emavoti abo eSenate naseNdlini yeTikhulu.
"Kuhlola liKhabhinethi kubaluleke kakhulu eluhlelweni lwemengameli kutsi njengobe sikhatsi sekukhankasela sesisondzele, utawuvakashela emave lamanyenti", kusho sikhulumi semkhankaso waTrump, lesingavumanga kutsi sitfunyelwe ligama lakhe  Reuters.
Umhlangano wemnyaka walamuhla eWesbanco Arena e Wheeling, e-Ohio, ePennsylvania, kanye nasePittsburgh, eWest Virginia, utawutsatsa sikhatsi lesidze.
NgaMgcibelo, Trump utawuvakashela eWest Virginia - live laphindze lawina ngalo ngemaphesenti langetulu kwa-40 nga-2016 - kwesibili ngenyanga leyengcile.
Trump wetama kusita umlingani wakhe waseWest Virginia lobitwa ngekutsi nguRiphabliki Patrick Morrissey, lophelelwa ngemandla elukhetfo.
"Akusilo luphawu loluhle kuMorrisey, uma umengameli eta kutomsekela elukhetfweni", kusho Simon Haeder, losati setembusave eNyuvesi yaseWest Virginia  Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Licembu laseMelika libonisa umoya wekulwa, ngekugcina litsemba lekuwina kuma-singles ngeLisontfo
Ngemuva kwetikhatsi letintsatfu tekuhlangana, indlela ye-foursome lebeyentiwa ngaMgcibelo ntsambama beyingaba nguloko lokudzingwa yi-Ryder Cup.
I-swinging swing ingumcondvo lowetayelekile wetemidlalo, kodvwa ngumcondvo lowenta badlali bakholwe kuwo, ikakhulukati emidlalweni lenjengalena.
Ngabe yini lesiyitsandzako nyalo?
"Baphetse emaphuzu lasitfupha, manje sebaphetse lamane, ngako-ke ngicabanga kutsi sinekuhamba kancane", kwasho Jordan Spieth.
Yebo, iYurophu ihamba embili ngemaphuzu lamane, kantsi kusasele emaphuzu lalishumi nakubili.
Kodvwa Spieth utsi bantfu baseMelika banemaphiko futsi banetibonelo tekulingisa, ikakhulukati kuSpieth naJustin Thomas, labadlala ndzawonye lilanga lonkhe futsi ngamunye wabo watfola emaphuzu lamatsatfu kulena lemine.
Spieth usongela yonkhe indzawo futsi ubeka sibonelo.
Lokukhala lokukhulu lokukhombisa injabulo kwachubeka kukhula ngesikhatsi sekugucuka kwakhe, kwafaka umfutfo lomkhulu, kwaphindze kwaphumelela lomdlalo ngesikhatsi yena na Thomas bahola emagoli lamabili ngemshayi munye.
Umphumela wekuhlanyela kwakhe, lokwaholela ekuncojeni kwabo ngemaphuzu langu-15, wahlangana nesikhalo lesifana nesitsi , lesisho kutsi licembu laseMelika lisengakhona.
"Kufanele wente konkhe lokusemandleni akho kutsi ukhatsateke ngemdlalo wakho", kwasho Spieth.
Nguloko lokusele kuloyo naloyo mdlali.
Imigodzi lengu-18 kuze kuncobiswe.
Emadvodza lamabili kuphela labeke ancoba Spieth naThomas kulamalanga lamabili lendlulile, nguFrancesco Molinari naTommy Fleetwood, indzaba lengeke iphikiswe yeRyder Cup.
Labangani labatsite labatsandzekako baseYurophu bancoba emacembu lamane, futsi bebangakukhohlisi loko.
"Moliwood" ngumndeni munye lowenta kahle kakhulu ngekungayifaki i-bogey ngemgcibelo, kodvwa waphindze wabalekela i-bogey ngemgcibelo ekuseni, ngeLesihlanu ntsambama kanye ne-back nine ngeLesihlanu ekuseni.
Indlela labadlala ngayo kanye nemandla lavelako ekudlala kanye nekuphuma esicukwini lesiphitsitelako, kukhombisa kutsi kufanele kutsi labadlali babhujiswe ngeLisontfo, nekutsi kute lomunye umdlali lofana naFleetwood nobe Molinari longenta kutsi licembu laseYurophu liphumelele kuLe Golf National.
Lokuncono kutsi basebentise emagumbi lamanyenti ngesikhatsi sinye.
Kodvwa-ke, kusesekuseni kakhulu kutsi ukhulume ngelikhono lelivela e-Europe.
Bubba Watson naWebb Simpson, bebayidlala ngekushesha iSergio Garcia, indvodza lebeyidlalela ema-fourball ekuseni, ngesikhatsi ahlangana na-Alex Noren.
Bogey kanye na-double double front nine, bavele bavala umgwaco emkhatsini wemSpanish neSweden, futsi abazange baphindze baphumelele.
NgeLisontfo kute umuntfu longasita kutsi sikhone kuphuma kulesigodzi.
I-Fourball ne-Foursome iyatsandzeka kakhulu ngenca yekubambisana kwebantfu labatsandzanako, seluleko labasinikako, neseluleko labangasiphili, kanye nendlela emacebo langashintja ngayo.
I-Europe beyisolo idlala kahle njengelicembu, futsi ibambe lichaza lelihle ngelilanga lekugcina, kepha lomdlalo wemine uphindze wakhombisa kutsi licembu laseMelika linentshisekelo yekulwa, lokwabekwa licala ngulabanye, ikakhulukati eMelika.
I-Europe seyiphumelele nga-10 kuya ku-6 futsi seyihola ngelilanga lekugcina le-Ryder Cup.
I-Europe inemandla lamakhulu ngelilanga lekugcina le-Ryder Cup ngemuva kwekuncoba ngemaphuzu lalishumi kuya kulasitfupha ngemidlalo ye-fourball kanye ne-foursome ngeMgcibelo ne-United States.
Umcimbi wacala nga-Tommy Fleetwood naFrancesco Molinari, labatsatsa umncintiswano wabo ngekutsi bancobe Tiger Woods, lokwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaphindze kwaba khona umncintiswano lomusha.
Licembu laseYurophu laThomas Bjorn, lebelifuna kugcina indondo lebeliyitfole eHazeltine eminyakeni lemibili leyendlulile, lacedza licembu laseMelika lebelihlose kwehlula, ngekuncoba umchudzelwano nga-3-1.
I-United States yabamba umzabalazo lomkhulu ku-foursome, yawina imidlalo lemibili, kodvwa beyingakhoni kukhokha.
Kute sigcine indondo, licembu laJim Furyko kufanele litfole emaphuzu lasiphohlongo kuma-singles langu-12 latawubanjwa ngeLisontfo.
Fleetwood ngumdlali wekucala wase Europe kutsi atfole emaphuzu lamane alandzelana, kantsi yena na Molinari (lelicembu labitwa ngekutsi yi "Molliwood" ngemuva kwemphelasontfo lejabulisako) babantfu lababili emlandvweni we Ryder Cup kutsi batfole emaphuzu lamane emidlalweni lemine yekucala.
Ngemuva kwekubamba boWoods naPatrick Reed ngemdlandla, behlulwa nguWoods kanye ne-American Bryson Dechambeau, batfola imiphumela lefanako, 5&4.
Woods, lowasebenta kakhulu ngemidlalo lemibili ngaMgcibelo, waveta emandla akhe ngalesinye sikhatsi, kepha kuze kube ngunyalo, sewulahlekelwe ngemidlalo lengu-19 ku-29 kuma-fourball kanye naku-foursome, leminye lemisikhombisa ilandzelana.
Justin Rose, lobekangekho ku-fourball yasekuseni, wabuyela ku-Henrik Stenson ku-foursome, wabamba Dustin Johnson naBrooks Koepka  labangu-1 kanye na-3 ngekulandzelana, ngemaphuzu lamabili nayinye.
Kodvwa-ke, kute lobekungajabulisa licembu laseYurophu ngalelo langa lelihle lelipholile, eningizimu-nshonalanga yeParis.
Umpetfu wemidlalo lemitsatfu, Jordan Spieth kanye naJustin Thomas, babeka umncele wemaMelika ngekutfola emaphuzu lamabili ngeMgcibelo.
Baphuma baphumelela 2&1 ku Jon Rahm wase Spain kanye na Ian Poulter ku Fourball base babuya emuva kuncoba Poulter na Rory McIlroy ku 4&3 ku Foursome, balahlekelwa ngemigodzi lemibili yekucala.
Kuphela tikhatsi letimbili emlandvweni weRyder Cup lapho licembu lelitawucedza khona ngekulahlekelwa ngemaphuzu lamane ngekucala li-single, nanobe licembu laFuryka belingamane lidlale ibhola lelitsite kute lihlale nalo.
Kodvwa-ke, njengobe bebabeka indzawo yesibili emalangeni lamabili lengcile, kubonakala shengatsi kuhlasela ngeLisontfo bekungeke kwenteke.
I-North Korea itsi akusiyo intfo yekungatihluphi, kodvwa kungatsembeki.
INdvuna Yetepolitiki yaseNyakatfo Korea yatsi ngesikhatsi ikhuluma kuUN, ngeMgcibelo kutsi kungahociswa kwetikhalo kungenta iMelika ingetsembi iNyakatfo Korea, futsi angeke ivele iyekele kusebentisa tikhali yayo te-nuclear.
Ri Yong Ho watsi ku-General Assembly yemnyaka, iNorth Korea yente "tinyatselo tekutitsandzela" kulomnyaka lophelile, njengekumisa luhlolo lwato lwekusebentisa i-nuclear kanye ne-missile, kucedza luhlolo lwato lwekusebentisa i-nuclear kanye nekutitsembisa kungatfutfuki ngetintfo te-nuclear.
"Kodvwa asikaboni kuphendvula lokucondzile kusuka eMelika", kwasho yena.
"Kute kwetsembela eMelika angeke kucinisekise kuvikeleka kwetfu, futsi angeke sikhone kucedza kuhlasela kweNyakatfo Korea".
Nanobe Ri aphindze waveta kukhonona kweNorth Korea mayelana nekungatsandzi kweWashington kutsi ivele ihambe kancane kancane, lapho khona iNorth Korea itawuvuzwa ngekwenta tinyatselo letichubekako, lesitatimende sakhe besibonakala sibalulekile ngobe besingakhombisi kutsi ilahla i-unilateral denuclearization, njengobe bekwentekile esikhatsini lesengcile.
Ri abekhuluma ngesitatimende lesisembili lesentiwa nguKim Jong Un kanye naDonald Trump ngesikhatsi semhlangano wekucala wemengameli waseMelika kanye nemholi waseNyakatfo Korea, lowaba seSingapore ngaJuni 12, ngesikhatsi Kim Jong Un atsintseka kutsi utawusebentela 'kucedza kusebenta ngetenhlavu yenyukliya eNhlonhlweni yaseKorea' kantsi Trump wetsembisa kucinisekisa kuphepha kweNyakatfo Korea.
I-North Korea beyilindzele kuphela kwesiphetfo semphi yase-Korea (ngemnyaka wa 1950 kuya ku 1953) kepha i-United States yatsi iPyongyang kumele inikele ngetikhali te-nuclear kucala.
I-Washington iphindze yawala ticelo tekunciphisa tikhalo leticinile temave emhlaba leticondziswe eNyakatfo Korea.
"IMelika icindzetela kutsi 'kucedvwe' i-nuclear, futsi ikhulisa umfutfo wayo ngetimali tekucindzetelwa kute ifinyelele umgomo wayo, iphindze iphikise ngisho nekusayina 'umculu wekuphela' kwemphi", kusho Ri.
"Lokucabanga kutsi tijeziso tingasiyekelisa umsebenti wetfu, kungumcabango webantfu labangati lutfo ngatsi.
Inkinga kutsi, nangabe singakhishwa lemisebenti, loko kungenta kutsi singetsembi labanye.
Ri akazange akhulume ngenchubomgomo yekuhlangana kwesibili kwaKim Jong Un naDonald Trump, lobekukhulunywe ngaye nguNdvunankhulu waseMelika ku-UN ekucaleni kweliviki.
Esikhundleni saloko, lomkhulumeli wacaphuna imihlangano lemitsatfu emkhatsini waKim Jong Un kanye na Moon Jae-in, umholi waseNingizimu Korea, etinyangeni letisihlanu letengcile, wase utsi: "Kube iNingizimu Korea, hhayi iMelika, beyingatsatsa luhlangotsi lwekucedza i-nuclear, ngabe lesicheme sekucedza i-nuclear sase-Korea asikafiki".
Ngetulu kwaloko, indlela Ri lakhuluma ngayo ayifani naleyo lakhuluma ngayo emhlanganweni we-UN ngemnyaka lowengcile, nakatsi kushaya i-raket yase-North Korea endzaweni yase-United States bekungeke kugwenywe ngemuva kwekutsi 'Mnu. Evil President' Trump abite Kim Jong Un ngekutsi 'ngu-rocket man' (umuntfu lonemrakethi) kulomsebenti wekutibulala.
Kulomhlangano we-UN, Trump, lowetsembisa kucedza i-North Korea ngalokuphelele emnyakeni lowengcile, wancoma Kim Jong-un ngekutitsatsa ngekutimisela tinyatselo tekucedza tikhali, kepha watsi kusekunyenti lokusamele kwentiwe, waphindze watsi kuze i-North Korea ibe ne-nuclear, tikhali angeke ticitfwe.
NgaLwesitsatfu, Trump watsi akazange abeke sikhatsi, watsi: "Kungakhatsaliseki kutsi kutsatsa iminyaka lemibili, iminyaka lemitsatfu nobe tinyanga letisihlanu, akunandzaba".
I-China neRussia batsi uMkhandlu weTekuphepha we-UN kumele umnike umklomelo Pyongyang ngenca yetinyatselo latitsetse.
Nanobe kunjalo, iNdvuna yeMbuso yaseMelika Mike Pompeo yatsi ku-UN Security Council ngaLesine: "Kuciniswa kwetigwebo te-UN Security Council kumele kuchubeke futsi kungapheli kute kube ngulapho sesibone kutsi sekute imphi lenkhulu, lephelele futsi lecinisekisiwe".
Kusukela nga-2006, uMkhandlu weTekuphepha weUN wacinisa tijeziso letimatima kuNorth Korea, etama kuvimbela imali ye-Pyongyang yetintfo te-nuclear kanye ne-ballistic missile.
Pompeo wahlangana naRi ngaphandle kwe-UN General Assembly, wase utsi utawuvakashela iPyongyang futsi ngenyanga letako, kute alungiselele umhlangano wesibili.
Pompeo sewuke wavakashela iNyakatfo Korea katsatfu kulomnyaka, kodvwa luhambo lwakhe lolwengetiwe alukabi yimpumelelo.
Washiya iPyongyang ngaJulayi, atsi kukhona lokwentiwako, kwatsi kungakapheli ema-awa lambalwa, iNorth Korea yamlahla ngekutsi "ufaka ticelo telicembu lebantfu labadvuna".
ENorth Korea, kuhlangana na Moon Jae-in kulenyanga, yetsembisa kutsi itawubhidlita indzawo yekuhlola imikhumbi kanye netakhiwo te nuclear uma ngabe iMelika itsatsa tinyatselo letifanele.
Watsi Kim Jong Un wamtjela kutsi "tindlela letifanele" labetitsandza kutsi atitsatse, nguleti: kucinisekisa kuphepha lokutsintswe nguTrump eSingapore kanye nekutsatsa tinyatselo tekucinisa budlelwane bakhe neWashington.
Bafundzi baseHarvard bafundza sifundvo sekuphumula sikhatsi lesidze
Kuleli, iHarvard University, yenta luhlelo lolusha lwekunika bonkhe bafundzi butfongo lobunyenti, kute kulwisane nemasiko lakhulako ebantfu labatsandza kufundza ngekusebentisa i-caffeine.
Bafundzi labasemayunivesithi laphakeme kakhulu emhlabeni bavame kungati kutsi kufanele batinakekele njani.
Charles Czeisler, longuphrofesa wemitsi yekulala eHarvard Medical School kanye nalosebenta esibhedlela iBrigham and Women's, wente luhlelo lalukhuluma ngekutsi lwekucala lolunjalo eMelika.
Wasungula leliklasi ngekunikela inkhulumo lemayelana nekungalali kahle kanye nemiphumela yako ekufundzeni.
 Ngemuva kwekusho lengcoco, intfombatana yeta kimi yafike yabuta,  "Kungani ungitjela loku nyalo, njengobe ngisonyakeni wekugcina esikolweni?"
Watsi kute umuntfu lowake wamtjela kutsi kusho kutsini kulala, loko kwangimangalisa", kusho The Telegraph.
Letifundvo, letentiwe kwekucala kulomnyaka, tifundzisa bafundzi kutsi imikhuba lemihle yekulala isita njani ekufundzeni nasetintfweni temidlalo, iphindze itsandze imphilo lenhle.
Paul Barreira, longuphrofesa wetemphilo yengcondvo eHarvard Medical School, kanye nemcondzisi lomkhulu wetemphilo kuleyonyuvesi, watsi lesifundvo sacala ngemuva kwekutsi kutfolakale kutsi bafundzi bebangakhoni kulala kahle evikini.
Letifundvo letifundvwako tingemalanga langu-10, futsi tifaka ekhatsi imisebenti lehlukahlukene lechutjwa ngekusebentisa tinhlelo tekuchumana.
Incenye yinye icuketse sitfombe sendzawo yekuhlangana lapho bafundzi bacofa khona ngetinkomishi tabo tenkhomo, emafasitelo, kufundza nekusebentisa umtimba kanye netincwadzi kute batfole lwati mayelana nekukhanyiswa kwekhefi, indlela kulahlekelwa butfongo lobunemandla ngayo kumdlalo, kanye nekubaluleka kwekulala njalo.
Kulomunye luhlangotsi, labantfu bafundza ngekutsi kulahlekelwa butfongo sikhatsi lesidze kungakhulisa njani ingoti yekufa kwesifo senhlitiyo, sifo semsheko, kucindzeteleka kanye nemdlavuza.
Lemephu ye-campus lenetitfombe letisebentisekako ikhutsata labakhona kutsi bacabangisise ngemisebenti yabo yemalanga onkhe.
Siyati kutsi loku angeke kusente sishintje indlela bafundzi labaphila ngayo.
Kodvwa siyakholwa kutsi banalo lilungelo lekwati  njengobe bonkhe bantfu banalo lilungelo lekwati ngemiphumela yekubhema, kwengeta Phrofesa Cheisler
Watsi: "Likoya lekufundza ebusuku solo likhona, kepha buchwephesha lobusha kanye nekucindzeteleka lokwandzako kwebafundzi kusho kutsi inkinga yekungalali kahle iyandza".
Kunika bafundzi butfongo lobunemphilo lobanele kufanele kube "sivikelo lesiyimfihlo" sekulwa nekucindzeteleka, kuphelelwa ngemandla kanye nekukhatsateka, futsi kungaphindze kusite ekuvimbeleni kukhuluphala, ngobe kungasebenti kahle kwebutfongo kwenta ingcondvo yakho ihambe ngendlela yekutsi ivele ilambe, lokwenta umfundzi ahlale alambile", washo njalo.
Raymond So, loseminyakeni lengu-19 budzala waseCalifornia lofundza ngekwakheka kwebantfu, waphindze wasita phrofesa Cheisler ekufundziseni leliklasi ngemuva kwekufundza kulelinye lamacembu akhe emnyakeni wakhe wekucala eHarvard.
Watsi lesikolwa samvula emehlo futsi samkhutsata kutsi afune kufundzisa bantfu lonkhe likolishi.
Lenyatselo lelandzelako, utsi, kutawuba kucela bonkhe bafundzi labasafundza ticu kutsi bacedze luhlelo lolufanako lwekuhlola ngaphambi kwekutsi baye kulesinye sikhungo.
Phrofesa Cheisler watjela bafundzi kutsi bafake ema-alamu labakhutsata kutsi balele futsi bavuke, waphindze watsi kufanele bati kutsi kukhanya kwe-LED kanye ne-elekthronikhi kuyingoti futsi kungenta bantfu bangakhoni kulala.
Live-ston 1-0 Rangers: Meng uyahlaselwa licembu laGerard
I-Ranger iphindze yahlupheka ngesikhatsi i-Livingston idlala, ngesikhatsi Dolly Meng ancoba licembu le-Steven Gerrard lebelihlulwe ngemadvolo, laze lalahlekelwa ngumdlalo nga-1 ku-1.
Lelicembu lase-Ibrox Stadium belitawuphumelela kwekucala kusukela nge-4-1 kuSt Johnstone ngaFebhuwari, kodvwa licembu laGary Holt lacedza Gerrard ngemidlalo lengu-18 kwesibili, lokwenta licembu lakhe lahlukana ne-Ladbrokes Premiership  Hearts ngemaphuzu lasiphohlongo.
Menga wafaka umgomo wakhe ngemizuzu lesikhombisa ngaphambi kwekuphela kwencenye yekucala, futsi lelicembu le-Ranger lebelibonakala lingakahlanganyeli belingabonakali lisatfutfuka.
Ngesikhatsi iRanger yehla yaba sesitsatfu, Livingston yenyuka yaya kwesitsatfu ngemuva kweHibernian, ngekulahlekelwa yinhloso yinye.
Licembu le-Ranger lingase libe netinkinga letengetiwe ngekufuna kwelapha umshayi-mtsetfo Calum Spence ngemuva kwekushaywa ngulenye intfo lebeyijikijelwe esiteji.
