"Umbuso waseMelika, ngemabutfo awo etemphi, unemandla ekucinisekisa kutsi tindlela telwandle tihlala tivulekile, futsi uma kudzingeka, uvimbela emandla awo kutsi angafiki emakethe", kwasho yena.
Zinke abekhuluma emcimbini lobewuhlelwe yi-Consumer Energy Alliance, lokuyinhlangano lengasebenti ngenzuzo, letibita ngekutsi yi-"Voice of the Energy Consumers" eMelika.
