"Kwetfula inkhulumo leyetfulwa bantfu, hulumende waseChina usebentisa emalungelo emaMelika ekuba nenkhululeko yekukhuluma kanye nekubhala inkhulumo lephephile ngekubeka sikhangiso lesikhokhelwako ku-Des Moines Register", kwabhala Branstad.
Kodvwa-ke, kute livoti lelingakhonjwa emgwacweni waseBeijing, futsi kute nekubonisa kahle imibono leyehlukene bantfu baseChina labanayo mayelana nekucondzisa umnotfo lokumangalisako lokwentiwa yiChina, njengoba imidiya ilawulwa kakhulu yi-Communist Party yaseChina.
Wengeta watsi lelinye lalamanye emaphephandzaba labalulekile ase China ala kushicilela sihloko sakhe, kepha akazange asho kutsi nguliphi.
Labasebentisana nabo bacaphele kutsi labesifazane labanelilungelo lekuvota bayababulala.
Njengobe emaRiphabliki lamanyenti labalulekile asekela aphindze avikela Brett Kavanaugh lobekwe esikhundleni sekuba nguSengameli wemajaji, lobhekene netinsolo tekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicasi, umhloli wecwayisa ngekutsi lamalunga emalunga emajaji atawuhlangabetana nekuphikiswa lokukhulu ngesikhatsi semikhankaso lelandzelako, ikakhulukati kubantfu labasikati.
Umphumela waloko waba kutsi bantfu labanyenti baseNingizimu Afrika bavele bacela kuvota.
"Loku angeke kuphindze kwenteke", kusho Grant Reeher, longuphrofesa wetemfundvo lemayelana netembusave e-Maxwell School lese-Syracuse University, encwadzini yakhe leyatfolakala ngaMgcibelo.
Reeher watsi akanalo litsemba lekutsi tinyatselo temalunga e-US, Jeff Flake (wase-Arizona) tekwenta luphenyo lolusembili lwe-FBI titawuncedza kucedza lulaka lwebavoti.
"Bafati angeke bakukhohlwe lokwentekile itolo, angeke bakukhohlwe kusasa futsi angeke bakukhohlwe kuze kube nguNovemba", kusho Karine Jean-Pierre, umeluleki lomkhulu kanye nesikhulumi savelonkhe se-MoveOn, ngeLesihlanu, kusho liphephandaba laseWashington.
NgaLesihlanu ekuseni, bamemeteli behlabela batsi "NgoNovemba uyefika" batfukutsele eholweni leSigungu saVelonkhe ngenca yesincumo seRiphabhulikhi lesengamele liKomiti Letebulungiswa sekungabuyisi kukhetfwa kwaKavanaugh nanobe Dokotela Christine Blasey Ford akhulume ngalendzaba, njengobe kwasho Mic.
"Lizinga lekushisekela inkhululeko yentsandvo yelinyenti kanye nesisusa sayo kutawugcwala kakhulu", kusho Stu Rothenberg, longumhlaziyi longakhetsi wetembusave, kulelinye likhasi le-news.
Bantfu batsi bekakadze amudze futsi loko kuliciniso.
Kodvwa lingaba liphakeme, ikakhulukati kubantfu labasikati labasemadolobheni labangafuni kuvota kanye nakulabo labasebasha labasemkhatsini weminyaka lengu-18 na-29 budzala, labangafuni kuvota, kodvwa labavamise kungamukeli.
Ngisho nangaphambi kwekutsi Ford afake bufakazi, lapho abeka khona imininingwane yetinsolo takhe tekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicasi, letibhekiswe kulona lofuna kuba lijaji leNkantolo lePhakeme, bacwaningi bebakhombisa kutsi uma emaRiphabhulikhi angatsatsa sincumo sekuvumela lomuntfu kutsi abe lijaji, loko bekungahle kubenetintfo letimatima.
"Lelicembu lemaRiphabhulikhi kumele libukane netinkinga letinkhulu", kusho Michael Steele, lobekangusihlalo we-Republican National Committee, ekucaleni kweliviki leliphelile, njengobe kubikwe yi-NBC News.
"Akusiyo nje kuphela incenye yelikomidi leliwadi, nobe incenye yekugcina, nobe ngabe Kavanaugh utawukhetfwa, kepha yindlela emaRiphabhulikhi layisebentise ngayo lendzaba nekutsi amtsatse njani Ford", kusho Guy Cecil, umcondzisi we Priorities USA, licembu lelisita kukhetfwa kwebaDemocrats.
Kodvwa-ke, bantfu baseMelika babonakala bahlukene kancane mayelana nekutsi ngubani lokufanele bamkholwe uma babhekene netimanga ta Ford na Kavanaugh, kantsi yena unekwesekelwa lokukhulu.
Luhlolo lolusha lwe-YouGov lukhombisa kutsi 41% walabaphendvulako bakholwa kakhulu nobe bavuma kutsi Ford ukhuluma liciniso, kantsi 35% bakholwa kakhulu nobe bavuma kutsi Kavanaugh ukhuluma liciniso.
Ngetulu kwaloko, 38% walabaphendvulwe batsi Kavanaugh kungenteka nobe kungenteka abetfuke ngesikhatsi afakaza, kantsi 30% kuphela lowatsi naye Ford abetfuke.
Ngemuva kwekucindzetelwa nguFlake, i-FBI yacala luphenyo mayelana netinsolo letashiwo ngu-Ford kanye nalomunye umshushisi lokutsiwa nguDeborah Ramirez, njengobe kubikwa yi-Guardian.
Ford wavuma ecaleni lakhe lebelifungelwe likomidi lebucotfo le-Senate kutsi Kavanaugh, ngesikhatsi anenkinga yekunatsa, wamshaya ngesikhatsi aneminyaka lengu-17 budzala.
