Umuntfu lowasungula i-World Wide Web uhlela kucala i-Internet lensha kute akwati kuchudzelana ne-Google ne-Facebook.
Tim Berners-Lee, losunguli we World Wide Web, usungula inkapani lefuna kuchudzelana ne Facebook, Amazon ne Google.
Umsebenti wekugcina walomdzala wetekhompyutha, Inrupt, yinkampani lesebenta ngemathuluzi lavulekile, i-Solid, leyentiwa yi-Berners-Lee.
I-Solid ivumela basebentisi kutsi bakhetse kutsi idatha yabo igcinwe kuphi nekutsi bobani labangakhona kutfola imininingwane letsite.
Ku-Fast Company, Berners-Lee watsi injongo yekwakha i-Inrupt "kukuhlola umhlaba".
"Kufanele sikwente nyalo", washo, abhekisa kulesitjalo lesisha.
"Sesifikile sikhatsi semlandvo".
Lolu hlelo lusebentisa buchwepheshe be-Solid platform kute bantfu bakhone kwakha "sitolo" sabo se-inthanethi lesinemininingwane yabo, nobe i-POD.
Loku kufaka ekhatsi luhlu lwetintfo lotidzingako, luhlu lwetintfo lotawenta, likhalenda, umtapo wemculo, naletinye tintfo lotisebentisako kanye naletisebentako.
Kufana ne-Google Drive, i-Microsoft Outlook, i-Slack kanye ne-Spotify, tonkhe tiphequluli tihlangene ngesikhatsi sinye.
Intfo leyehlukile ngesitolo lesiku-inthanethi lesine-data yakho kutsi nguyiphi imininingwane longayifinyelela lesetandleni temsebentisi.
Le-Intanethi ikubita ngekutsi "kuniketwa emandla ngekwemuntfu ngekusebentisa idatha".
Ngekuya kwa-CEO we-Solid, John Bruce, umgomo we-Inrupt kutsi unikete bantfu imitfombolusito, tinchubo kanye nemakhono lafanele kute kusitwe kutsi sisebenti se-Solid sifinyeleleke kubo bonkhe bantfu.
Nyalo le-company ifaka ekhatsi i-Berners-Lee, i-Bruce, intfo yekuphepha leyatsengwa yi-IBM, kanye nalabanye batfutfukisi labacashwe kutsi basebente kulomklamo, kanye nemphakatsi webantfu labavolontiya.
Kusukela kuleliviki, bakhi betinsita emhlabeni wonkhe bakwati kwakha tinhlelo tabo tekusebentisa emandla lavela ku-inrupt.
Berners-Lee watsi yena nelicembu lakhe abakakhulumi ne-Facebook ne-Google mayelana nekwenta lushintjo lolukhulu lolutawugucula imodeli yabo yebhizinisi ngalokuphelele.
"Angibati kutsi ngicela imvume".
Kulesihloko lesishicilelwe ngeMgcibelo ku-Medium, Berners-Lee wabhala kutsi "umsebenti we-Inrupt kuniketa emandla etekuhweba kanye netinhlelo tekusebenta kute kusite kuvikela kucina kanye nekhwalithi yelinethiwekhi lensha leyakhiwe nge-Solid".
Nga-1994 Berners-Lee washintja i-Internet ngesikhatsi asungula i-World Wide Web Consortium eMassachusetts Institute of Technology.
Etinyangeni letimbalwa letendlulile, Berners-Lee bekafaka sandla kakhulu enkhulumeni lemayelana nekungatingeni etintfweni letitsite.
Ngekubeka Inrupt Berners-Lee utawuhlala angumsunguli kanye nemcondzisi we World Wide Web Consortium, iWeb Foundation kanye ne Open Data Institute.
"Ngijabula kakhulu ngekucabanga ngelikusasa lelihle lenethiwekhi", kwengeta Berners-Lee.
