Umholi welicembu le-Venetian, uMnumzane Bernard Vann, wahlonishwa ngelilanga le-29 enyangeni yeNyoni nga-1918 ngekuhlasela iBellenglise neLehaucourt.
Wabulawa ngumuntfu lobekabulala ngemakhasi emaphoyisa ngemuva kwemalanga lamane, angakaze atfole kutsi uniketwe umklomelo lomkhulu waseBrithani.
