Ngekusho kwe-London Gazette, nga-September 29, 1918, inkhosi Vann yahola libutfo layo lemasotja lelihamba emfuleni i-Saint-Quentin, "emkhatsini wemabomu lamanyenti kanye nekuhlasela lokukhulu lokwakwentiwa ngemaphini kanye nangemachinga".
Wase uyagijima uya emgceni wekulwa, "ngesibindzi lesikhulu" wahola lomkhosi, wase uhlasela tindzawo temabutfo emphi, wabulala lamatsatfu awo.
Vann wabulawa ngumuntfu lobekabulala emaJalimane nga-October 4, 1918, lokwacishe kwaba yinyanga ngaphambi kwekutsi imphi iphele.
