Lomdlali we-Olimpiki we- bronze kabili, sewukhule waba ngumuntfu lofuna kuvikela bantfu labangafuni kuhlanganyela e-LGBT, futsi usebentise loko lakushoko emidlalweni ye-Commonwealth kulomnyaka e-Australia, kute ancenge emave lamanyenti kutsi asuse bugebengu lobentiwa bantfu labangafuni kuhlanganyela e-LGBT.
