Umkhumbi lomusha wemaJalimane wekulwa uphindze wahlehliswa
I-German Navy's newest frigate kufanele isebente nga-2014 kute itsatse sikhundla semikhumbi yemphi leseyigugile yasendvulo, kepha angeke isebente kuze kube nguNyoni ngenca yemiklamo lephukile kanye netindleko letikhulako , njengoba kubikwe ngemaphephandzaba asekhaya.
Umkhumbi lomkhulu we-Baden-Wuerttemberg class frigate, i-Rheinland-Pfalz, sewutawucala kusebenta ngenyanga yeNgongoni 2019, kusho liphephandzaba i-Die Zeit, ngekusho kwesikhulumi sembutfo wetemphi.
Lomkhumbi bekumele ufakwe ku-Navy nga-2014, kepha tinkinga letenteka ngemuva kwekutfunyelwa kwatsiwa kumele kwentiwe tingucuko kulomklamo lohlose kakhulu.
Emathuluzi lamane emaBaden-Wuerttemberg latawutsatsa sikhundla semabutfo emphi nga-2007 atawutsatsa sikhundla semabutfo emphi lase Bremen lasakhulile.
Kuliciniso kutsi, titawuba nemabutfo lanemandla, tinhlobo letehlukene tetindiza letingaphindzi tibonakale kanye netinhlelo tebuchwepheshe tekungaboni, lokufaka ekhatsi kwehlisa emagugu e-radar, infrared kanye ne-acoustic.
Letinye tintfo letibalulekile tifaka ekhatsi sikhatsi lesidze emkhatsini wekunakekelwa  kusebenta kwemikhumbi lensha kumele kube khona ngisho iminyaka lemibili ngaphandle kwemikhumbi yemikhumbi.
Kodvwa, kubambezeleka lokungapheli kusho kutsi lemikhumbi yetimphi yesimanje, lekumele isite emaJalimane kutsi aphendvule etimeni tangaphandle, itawube seyiphelelwe sikhatsi uma seyicala kusebenta  kubika i-Die Zeit.
Le F125 lebeyiyindzala kakhulu yavela emakhasi lasetulu emaphephandzabeni emnyaka lowengcile, ngesikhatsi le Nkhumbi Yemanti yaseJalimane ivuma kutsi ingasebenti futsi yabuyiselwa eBlohm & Voss eHamburg.
Bekungokokuqala ngca kutsi umkhumbi wemphi ubuyiselwe emuva emkhombeni wekutfutsa imikhumbi.
Bekungatiwa lokuningi ngetizatfu tekutsi kungani lomkhumbi wehluleka kusebenta, kepha ema media aseJalimane abika ngetintfo letibalulekile letenteka ku-software kanye naku-hardware letenta kutsi lomkhumbi ungabi lusito emphini.
Letinkinga teluhlelo tentiwe taba nguletinkhulu kakhulu, ngobe imikhumbi yeBaden-Wuerttemberg kumele isetjentiswe ngemalunga emkhumbi lalinganiselwa ku-120, lokusho kutsi incenye yemkhumbi lomncane kunemikhumbi lendzala yeBremen.
Kwavela nekutsi lenkhumbi isindvwa kakhulu, lokwenta kutsi ingakhoni kusebenta kahle futsi kuvimbela kutsi imikhumbi yemphi ingakhoni kwenta tingucuko esikhatsini lesitako.
Lomkhumbi lowesindzako longemathani langu 7000, iRheinland-Pfalz, ucishe ube ngu-2 000 ngemathani, futsi ucishe ube sinyenti kunemikhumbi lefanako lebeyisetjentiswa ngemaJalimane emphini yesibili yemhlaba.
Ngaphandle kwemathuluzi langakalungi, inkinga iphindze ibe yindleko yalo lonkhe leprojekthi  kufaka ekhatsi kuceceshwa kwebasebenti.
Kubikwa kutsi lemali seyifinyelele ezingeni lelisetulu le-EUR 3,1 billion (USD 3,6 billion) ngesikhatsi lemali yekucala beyi-EUR 2,2 billion.
Tinkinga tekwetfula imikhumbi lensha yekulwa ticala kuba nemandla kakhulu ngenca yeticwayiso letisandza kwentiwa tekutsi umkhumbi wemaJalimane uyacitseka.
Ekucaleni kwalomnyaka, Hans-Peter Bartels, umengameli weliKhomishani Letekuvikela leliKhomishani lePhalamende laseJalimane, wavuma kutsi imikhumbi yemabutfo aseJalimane "itawube seyiphelile" uma ngabe ingasebenti.
Waphindze watsi inkinga ikhule ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi ngenca yekukhishwa kwetikhumbi letindzala ngaphandle kwekuniketa tikhumbi tekusebenta.
Waphindze waveta kutsi bekangakutsandzi kutsi kute ngisho munye lowakhona kulelicembu le Baden-Wuerttemberg lowakhona kujoyina imikhumbi yemanti.
