Brexit: UK ngaso sonkhe sikhatsi beyifisa kutsi labakhiqizi betimoto bahambe
INdvuna yeBhizinisi, Greg Clark, itsi iBrithani itawutilahla kuze kube phakadze uma ingaphindze ibe ngumholi wemhlaba wekukhicita timoto ngemuva kwekuphuma kwayo ku-EU.
Wengeta watsi "bekakhatsatekile" ngesikhatsi ummeleli weToyota UK akhuluma ne-BBC atsi uma i-UK ishiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano, umkhicito ku-Burnaston, edvute nase Derby, utawumiswa kwesikhashana.
"Sidzinga kucocisana", kwasho Clark.
Lomunye ummeleli wemkhicito wetimoto waseJapan watsi kubambezeleka emnyeleni uma kungaphumeleli kucedza sicelo se-Brexit kungenta kutsi kube nekuncishiswa kwemisebenti.
Lefektri yaseBurnaston, lapho kwakhiwa khona iAuris ne-Avensis, yakhicita timoto letingu 150 000 ngemnyaka lophelile, 90% wato watitfumela kulamanye emave e-European Union.
"Ngicabanga kutsi uma i-UK ingakhipha sivumelwano e-EU ekupheleni kwenyanga yeNdlovulenkhulu, kutawuba nekuma lokukhulu ekwakhiweni kwetintfo letitfolakala lapha eBurston", kusho Marvin Cooke, umphatsi we-Toyota eBurston.
Labanye bakhiciti bemoto base UK besaba kushiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano sendlela yekuhweba ngetindlela letingafani, kufaka ekhatsi iHonda, iBMW neJaguar Land Rover.
Sibonelo, iBMW itawuvala imboni yayo ye-Oxford ye-Mini ngemuva kwenyanga ye-Brexit.
Tinkinga letinkhulu tihlobene  njengobe bakhiciti bemoto bakusho  netingoti letingaba khona kuletinhlelo tekuphakela uma ngabe i-UK ishiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano.
Umkhicito we-Toyota usebenta ngesimiso se-just-in-time, lapho khona tincenye tifika njalo ngemaminitsi langu-37 kusuka kubatsengisi base-UK kanye nase-EU uma kwentiwa imoto lehloselwe bantfu.
Uma i-UK ishiya i-EU ngaphandle kwesivumelwano mhlaka-29 kuMashi, kutawuba netinkinga emnyeleni, lokungaholela ekutseni kube nekubambezeleka kanye nekushoda kwetincenye temkhicito.
Lomunye ummeleli walenkampani watsi, iToyota angeke ikhone kuhlala lilanga linye ingakatfoli tintfo tekuyitsenga kulelikhampani lase Derbyshire, ngako-ke umkhicito utawumiswa.
Clark watsi luhlelo lwa Theresa May lwekuhlola budlelwane be EU busembili "luhlelwe kahle kutsi lunganaki kuhlolwa kwemincele".
"Sidzinga sivumelwano. Sifuna sivumelwano lesincono kakhulu lesingeke nje sigcine ngekutfola injabulo lenkhulu lesinayo kodvwa siphindze sisisebentise kahle lesimo", kusho yena kuloluhlelo lwe-BBC Radio 4 namuhla.
Titatimende letingaveli ku-Toyota kuphela, kodvwa nakuletinye tikhampani tikhombisa kutsi kudzingeka kutsi sikhone kuchubeka naloko bekusebenta kahle kakhulu.
Lelihhovisi le-Toyota alikwazanga kukhomba kutsi umkhicito utawumiswa sikhatsi lesingakanani, kodvwa lacaphela kutsi esikhatsini lesidze, letindleko letengetiwe titawenta kutsi lelihhovisi lingakhoni kuchudzelana futsi loko kutawusho kutsi bantfu labatawucala kusebenta bayodzinwa.
Peter Tsouvallaris losebente eBurnaston iminyaka lengu-24 futsi lolilunga le-United union, watsi emalunga aleyo nyunyana akhatsateke kakhulu: "Ngati kutsi uma ngabe kulahleka imisebenti angeke iphindze ibuye.
Sikhulumi sahulumende satsi: 'Sivete luhlelo lolucondzile nalolunebungako lobutawuba khona ngebudlelwane betfu ne-European Union'.
Umhlangano waTrump naRosenstein ungahle ucitselwe eceleni futsi, kusho iWhite House
Umhlangano lobalulekile waDonald Trump neSekela leMengameli weTemtsetfo Rod Rosenstein ungahle 'ubekwe' ngemuva kweliviki ngenca yekulwa lokungapheli kwe-Brett Kavanaugh, umbekwacala weNkantolo lePhakeme, i-White House yatsi ngeLisontfo.
Rosenstein wengamela umsebenti weMshushisi Lomkhulu Robert Mueller, lohlolisisa kungenelela kwebantfu baseRussia elukhetfweni, kuchumana kwebantfu labakhulu labadvuna baTrump neRussia, kanye nekubangela umtsetfo kutsi ungaphumeleli.
Kutsi ngabe Trump utawucedza liSekela leMengameli, bese usongela inkhululeko yaMueller, sekuphele tinyanga letimbalwa kuhlotjiswe indzaba lematima eWashington.
Ekucaleni kwalenyanga, i-New York Times yabika kutsi Rosenstein ukhulume ngekubamba lihele kute akwati kucocela Trump, kanye nangendlela yekumbamba esikhundleni ngekulandzela luCwebu lwema-25.
Rosenstein waphika kutsi loku kungumlandvo.
Kodvwa ngeMsombuluko lowengcile, waya eNdlini leMhlophe ngenca yetindzaba tekutsi utawutsatsa sikhundla sakhe.
Umhlangano waTrump, lobekahlala e-UN eNew York ngaleso sikhatsi, wabekwa ngeLesine.
Trump watsi angatsandza kumcosha Rosenstein, kodvwa loko kwaletsa kutsi kube nesikhatsi lesidze sekuhlangana, kuze kungabi khona lokuchumanisa kuhlolwa kwe-Senate Judiciary Committee, lapho khona Kavanaugh kanye nalomunye walabesifazane labamsola ngekumhlukubeta, Dkt Christine Blasey Ford.
NgaLesihlanu, Trump wayala kutsi kube neluphenyo lweli-FBI lolwalutawutsatsa liviki lonkhe mayelana netinsolo letatentiwe kuKavanaugh, lokwabuye kwalibambelela livoti le-Senate.
Umkhulumeli wa Trump, Sarah Sanders, wavela ku Fox News ngeLisontfo.
Watsi nakabutwa kutsi utawuhlangana yini naRosenstein, watsi: "Sikhatsi sekuhlangana solo asikateki, kungenteka kutsi sekutawuba kuleliviki, nobe kungenteka kutsi sekutawuba ngulomunye liviki, ngenca yetintfo letenteka eNkantolo lePhakeme".
Asesibone, ngitawuvele ngishumayele.
Labanyenti batfukutsele batsi Sanders akazange abambe inkhulumo yetindzaba yeNdlu yeMhlophe kusukela ngaSeptemba 10.
Umhlahlandlela Chris Wallace wabuta kutsi kungani.
Sanders watsi lemincane inombolo yetinkhulumo bekungasiko kutsi bekangabatsandzi babhali bethelevishini labatsandza kuba ngito, wase utsi: "Ngingeke ngikufihle kutsi bona batitsandza kakhulu".
Wase utsi kutawukhula kuchumana emkhatsini waTrump nebatfumeli betindzaba.
"Mengameli lomusha wente imibuto leminyenti kunanobe ngumuphi lomunye umengameli", kwasho yena, angakachazi kutsi: "Sati kahle tinombolo".
