Luhlolo lolwentiwe kubantfwana besikolwa labangetulu kwalabangu-20 000 lutfole kutsi kunekukhula lokukhulu kwema-Instagram fake
Letindzaba tikhulise kukhatsateka ngekutsi ku-internet kunetindzaba letitsite letitsintsa umtimba.
Emaphesenti langu-20 ebafundzi atsi banayo i-akhawunti yabo "lemcoka" labayikhombisa batali babo
Umntfwana munye kulabasihlanu  labanye baneminyaka lengu-11 budzala  uvula ema-akhawunti ekuchumana angawatjeli bantfu labadzala.
Luhlolo lolwentiwe kubantfwana labasetulu kwetikolwa temabanga laphakeme letingu-20 000 lukhombisa kukhula lokukhulu kwe-akhawunti ye-Instagram.
Letindzaba tikhulise kukhatsateka ngekutsi lama-akhawunti asetjentiselwa kutfumela tindzaba telicansi.
Emaphesenti langu-20 ebafundzi avuma kutsi banema-akhawunti abo labamnyama labakhombisa batali babo, futsi aphindze abe nema-akhawunti abo langasese.
Lomunye make lowatfola likhasi lelingasese lendvodzakati yakhe leneminyaka lengu-13 budzala, wahlangana nalenye intfombatana lebeyitsandza kutsi idlwengulwe.
Lucwaningo lolwentiwe etikolweni letitimele ngu-Digital Awareness UK kanye ne-Headmasters' and Headmistresses' Conference (HMC) lutfole kutsi bafundzi labangemaphesenti langu-40 beminyaka lengu-11 kuya ku-18 banemaphrofayili lamabili, futsi ihhafu yabo ivuma kutsi inemakhodi abo.
Mike Buchanan, longumengameli we-HMC, utsi: "Kukhatsateka kutsi bantfu labanyenti labaseminyakeni yekutfomba bakha tindzawo tabo ku-Internet lapho batali babo kanye nabothishela bangeke bakhone kubatfola khona".
