Nati letinye tintfo letibalulekile mayelana nelidolobha lasePalu kanye nelidolobha laseDonggala esichingini saseCelebes:
Palu yindzawo lenkhulu yase Celebes Central, esifundzeni lesisekugcineni kweligede lelimfisha lelisentshonalanga yelwandle, inebantfu labangu 379 800 nga 2017.
Ngesikhatsi lesihlahla sigadla, bekusikhatsi sekugubha iminyaka lengu-40 kusukela sakhiwa.
Donggala yi kabupaten (inhlangano lephansi kunesifundza) lesendlula ngetulu kwemakhilomitha lamakhulu lamatsatfu ngasenyakatfo-nshonalanga yelwandle.
Kubalwa kwebantfu labangu-299 200 nga-2017.
Umnotfo we Central Celebes usebenta ngekudla timfishi kanye nekulima, lokuyintfo lematima kakhulu endzaweni yase Donggala.
Lomunye umtfombo wemali yesifundza ngumayini we nickel, kepha loku kutfolakala kakhulu eMorowali, leseceleni kwelwandle lweCelebes.
I-Indonesia Disaster Management Agency itsi, kuleminyaka lelikhulu leyendlulile, Palu neDonggala sekube netihlekelele temhlaba kanye nema-tsunami.
Nga-1938, i-tsunami leyahlasela eDonggala yabulala bantfu labangetulu kwa-200 futsi yabhidlita emakhaya lamanyenti.
Nga-1996, i-tsunami leyabulala bantfu labangu-9 e-Donggali leseNtshonalanga.
I-Indonesia isendzaweni lenetikhukhula letinyenti, futsi loku kwenta kutsi kutamatama kwemhlaba kube khona njalo.
Kuhlaselwa lokukhulu kwemhlaba kanye ne-tsunami eminyakeni lembalwa leyengcile:
2004: Kuhlasela kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwenteka ngaDecember 26 e Aceh, esifundzeni sase Aceh, enyakatfo yeSumatra, kwabangela tsunami leyahlaselwa emaveni langu-14 yabulala bantfu labangu 226 000 elugwini lweLwandle lweNdiya, ngetulu kwehhafu yabo e Aceh.
2005: Ekupheleni kwaMarch kanye nasekucaleni kwa-April, kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kwahlasela insimu yaseSumatra lesentshonalanga.
Bantfu labanyenti bafa esichingini saseNias, lesiselugwini lwaseSumatra.
2006: Eningizimu yeJava, lokuyisichingi lesinebantfu labanyenti e-Indonesia, kwaba nekutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwabangela i-tsunami leyahlasela ngaseningizimu, kwabulala bantfu labangu-700.
2009: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokunemandla la-7.6 kwahlasela edvute nePadang, lokulidolobha lelikhulu laseWest Sumatra.
Bantfu labangetulu kwa-1100 bafa ngenca yaloko.
2010: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokungu-7.5 kwahlasela sihlenge saseMentawai lesingaselugwini lwaseSumatra, kwabangela kutsi kube ne-tsunami lenemamitha langu-10 budze, leyabhubhisa emadolobhana lamanyenti futsi yabulala bantfu labangu-300.
2016: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokuncane kuhlasela iPidie Jaya, esifundzeni sase-Aceh, kubangela konakala nekwesaba kubantfu labasakhumbula umonakalo lowentiwe kutamatama kwemhlaba lokwabulala bantfu kanye ne-tsunami yanga-2004.
Ngalesikhatsi, bekungekho tsunami, kodvwa takhiwo letishayisana nato tabulala bantfu labangetulu kwa-100.
2018: Kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu kwahlasela sihlenge lesivakashelwa e-Indonesia, iLombok, kwabulala bantfu labangetulu kwa-500, ikakhulukati enyakatfo.
Kwabhidlita tindlu letinyenti futsi kwabangela tinkhulungwane tebavakashi tinkinga tesikhashana.
Indvodzana yaSara Palin lendzala iboshwa ngelicala lekudlwengulwa
Track Palin, indvodzana lendzala yembusi wangaphambilini wase-Alaska kanye nalokhetfwe kutsi abe nguphakatsi kwebantfu lababili, Sarah Palin, uboshelwe licala lekushaya umuntfu.
Ngekusho kwembiko lokhishwe nguLesibili yi-Alaska State Troopers, lomuntfu loneminyaka lengu-29 budzala wase-Alaska wase-Wasillah, waboshwa ngetigameko letimbi tekuhlukunyetwa emakhaya, kuphatamiseka ekubikeni, kanye nekumelana nekuboshwa.
Umbiko wemaphoyisa utsi ngesikhatsi umngani walosolwa etama kubita emaphoyisa kutsi afake sicelo sekwenta licala, lomsolwa watsatsa lucingo lwakhe.
KTUU itfule kutsi Palin uhlala ejele lemat-Su, futsi ubekelwe imali lengu-R500.
Ngekusho kwemniningwano wakhe, wavela enkantolo ngeMgcibelo lowengcile, lapho khona atsi "ngicinisile anginacala".
Palin unelicala lelibitwa ngekutsi ngu-A, lokusho kutsi angahle atfole sigwebo semnyaka munye ejele kanye nemali lelinganiselwa ku-R250.000.
Waphindze wabekwa licala lelibitwa ngekutsi licala lesigaba B, lelihambisana nelicala lekugwetjwa lilanga linye kanye nelicala lekukhokhiswa inhlawulo lengu-R3 000.
Akusilo kwekucala Palin abekwa emacala ebugebengu.
NgaDisemba 2017, wabekwa licala lekuhlasela babe wakhe, Todd Palin.
Ngulapho make wakhe, Sarah Palin, abita khona emaphoyisa kutsi ambikele ngalokushaywa.
Lelicala nyalo selisesiKhotho seTikhalo temaVeterans sase-Alaska.
NgaJanuwari 2016, wabekwa emacala ekuhlukunyetwa ngekwemindeni, kuphatamisa kubika kanye nekuphatsa sibhamu angakanaki, macondzana naloku.
Umngani wakhe utsi wamshaya ebusweni.
Nga-2016, emacembu ebantfu labadzala agceka Sarah Palin ngekuhlanganisa kutiphatsa lokuneludlame kwendvodzana yakhe ne-PTSD layitfola ngesikhatsi ase-Iraq.
Bantfu Labakhulu Babulawa Ngu-tsunami Ngemuva Kwekuzamazama Kwemhlaba E-Indonesia
Lokungenani bantfu labangu-384 babulawa kutamatama kwemhlaba lokwahlasela sihlenge saseCelebes e-Indonesia.
Loku kwabangela kutamatama kwemhlaba lokukhulu lokwabangela kutsi kube ne-tsunami futsi kwabhubhisa tindlu letinyenti.
Kucitseka kwebantfu labashonile, kanye nekungakhoni kusebentisa gezi netekuchumana, kulindzeleke kutsi kukhule ngetulu kwemalanga lambalwa letako.
Kuhlaselwa kwaletindzawo bekusendzaweni lesedvute neCelebes Island, lengasenyakatfo-mpumalanga yeJakarta, lokulidolobha lelikhulu lase-Indonesia.
Ema-video lakhombisa lesimo sekwehluleka kwemhlaba ayandza etinhlelweni tekuchumana.
Ngesikhatsi kugadla lomfula, bantfu labanyenti bebakhona elugwini lwasePalu lapho bekubanjwe khona lomkhosi.
Umshushisi wahulumende ufuna kutsi kujeziswe umuntfu lowesolwa ngekuhlaselwa ngebugebengu eNew York.
Bamangali baseNew York bafuna kutsi kujeziswe Saipov ngelicala lekufa ngenca yekuhlaselwa ngemaphekula lokwabulala bantfu labangu-8 eNew York, lokuyintfo lengakavami leyenteka kulelive kusukela nga-1953.
Kulomhlaka-ngci, Saipov, loneminyaka lengu-30 budzala, wahlasela emabhayisikili labehamba ngebuhlalu be West Side Highway eManhattan, futsi bekutsiwa usebentisa iloli yakhe yekuboleka lebeyivela ku Home Depot, futsi wabulala bantfu labahamba ngetinyawo kanye nebagibeli bemabhayisikili.
Ngekuya kwesatiso lesikhishwe yi-SAD, kutsi uma ngabe bantfu bafuna kujeziswa ngekufa, umshushisi utawudzinga kutsi akhombise kutsi Saipov ubulale bantfu labangu-8 ngemabomu nekutsi wabangela kulimala lokukhulu.
Ngekusho kwemaphepha enkantolo, totimbili letizatfu tifaka ekhatsi kufa.
Emavikini lambalwa ngemuva kwalokuhlasela, lijaji le-Federal Court laletsa Saipov emacala langu-22, lafaka ekhatsi emacala lasiphohlongo ekubulala umuntfu ngekwenta umsebenti longekho emtsetfweni , lokuyindlela leyetayelekile yebatfutsi bemajaji bahulumende bemave ngemave etindzabeni tebugebengu lobuhlelekile  kanye nelicala lebudlova nekubhubhisa timoto.
Umshushisi watsi lokuhlasela bekudzinga "kuhlelwa lokucinile nekucondziswa" futsi indlela Saipov layenta ngayo loko "yayingakalungi, inelunya futsi ingasiko kwemtsetfo".
 Sayfullo Habibullaevic Saipov uletse kuhlupheka, umonakalo kanye nekulahlekelwa emindenini kanye nakubangani ba Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erli, Hernán Ferrucci, Hernán Diego Mendoza kanye na-Alejandro Damian Pagnucca  utsi sitatimende sekuhlela.
Labasihlanu kulabantfu labafa bekubahlali base-Argentina lebebavakashele iNew York.
Kugwetjwa kwekufa lokwendlulele eSouthern District yaseNew York kwacala eminyakeni lelishumi leyendlulile.
Umsolwa Khalid Barnes watfolakala anelicala lekubulala lababili labahlinzeki betidzakamiva, kepha wagcina atfole sigwebo sekuhlala aphila ngaSeptemba 2009.
Sicatfulo sekufa lesentiwa yi federal case sagcina kwentiwa eNew York ngemnyaka wa 1953 ku Julius na Ethel Rosenberg. Umshado wabo wacitfwa ngemuva kwekubanjwa licala lekudlela emacala ekuhlelela kanye nekusebentela iSoviet Union ngesikhatsi se Cold War.
Bobabili boRosenberg babulawa ngogesi ngaJuni 19, 1953.
Emaphepha enkantolo aveta kutsi Saipov, lochamuka e-Uzbekistan, akazange avume kutsi kunenkinga yembeza etinyangeni letimbalwa ngemuva kwalokuhlaselwa.
Emaphoyisa atsi watjela baphenyo kutsi utiva kahle ngaloko lakwenta.
Ngekusho kwemtsetfo, Saipov wavuma kuhulumende kutsi wavuselelwa ngema-video e-ISIS labekabukele efonini yakhe.
Emaphoyisa atsi waphindze wafuna kutsi kubekwe ifulegi ye-ISIS egumbini lakhe lasesibhedlela.
Uphikisana netimanga letingu-22 letitsi yena akenti lutfo.
David Patton, longulomunye webavikeli betemtsetfo bendzabuko labamelela Saipov, watsi "ngalokusobala badvumatekile ngesincumo seMshushisi".
"Sitsatsa sincumo sekufuna kufa kanye nekulahlwa kwesigwebo semphilo yonkhe ngaphandle kwekukhululeka ngaphambi kwesikhatsi uma ngabe uvuma licala, sitotfutfukisa kuhlupheka lokubangelwe nguletintfo kubo bonkhe labatsintsekako", kwasho yena.
Licembu lemalunga laSaipov lacela kutsi umshushisi angasifuni sigwebo sekufa.
Lilunga le-Torus litsi NIGEL FARAGE kumele atsatse umtfwalo wekubonisana nge-Brexit
Emkhankasweni wemhlangano we-Torry lamuhla, Nigel Farage wetsembisa kutsi utawuletsa "libutfo lebantfu".
Lomunye lobekangumholi we UKIP watsi bosopolitiki kumele "bativa bashaywa ngetinhloko" ngema-euroceptics, ngesikhatsi lomunye webahlali basePhalamende baka Theresa May atsi kumele atsatse umtfwalo wekubonisana ne-EU.
Peter Bone, lilunga le-Treaty, watjela bantfu lebebabhikisha eBirmingham kutsi kube Farage bekangumbhali we-Brexit, "i-UK ngabe seyivele ingekho ku-EU".
Kodvwa-ke, kuhlanganyela kwebantfu labatsandza kuhlala e-UK emicimbini leyehlukene yekumelana ne-Brexit edolobheni, kukhombisa kakhulu umtfwalo lobukene na-Theresa May wekuhlanganisa emacembu akhe lahlukene.
Lomake, Ndvunankhulu, usebente kamatima kute ente lisu lakhe lekuyekela kubhema neChequers libe yimphumelelo, kantsi kuhlasela lokwentiwa ngulabo labatsandza kuphuma e-EU, labangafuni kuphuma e-EU kanye nalabo labangafuni kuphuma e-EU.
Labasekelako batsi, nanobe baphikiswa, utawufuna kufinyelela esivumelwaneni neBrussels, bese uphocelela bantfu labangavumelani ne-EU kanye ne-Labour kutsi bakhetse emkhatsini waloko lakushoko kanye ne "Chaos".
Peter Bone utsite emhlanganweni we-Leave Means Leave eSolihull kutsi ufuna "kulahla" luhlelo lwe-Chequers.
Washo kutsi Nigel Farage kumele abe nguPhoyisa, futsi kumele anikwe umtfwalo wekubonisana neBrussels.
"Kube bekunguye lobekasebenta, ngabe sesiphelelwe ngumhlaba nyalo", kwasho yena.
Lelinye lilunga le-Wellingborough le-MP laphindze latsi: "Ngiyayisekela i-Brexit, kodvwa kufanele siyekele luhlelo lwe-Chequers".
Akhuluma ngekuphikisana kwakhe ne-European Union, watsi: "Asikayilwi timphi temhlaba kuze sitfole emandla.
Sifuna kuba nemalungelo etfu eveni letfu.
Peter Bone wawala imibono yekutsi bantfu bashintje indlela labacabanga ngayo ngemuva kwekuvota nga-2016: "Loku kutsi bantfu baseBrithani bashintje indlela labacabanga ngayo futsi bafuna kuhlala e-EU akusilo liciniso".
Lomunye lobekakhona emkhosini bekungu-Andrea Jenkyns, lobekafuna kuphuma e-UK, lowatsi kubentatimende: "Make PM, lalela bantfu.
Lelisu le-Chequers alitsandvwa ngumphakatsi, liphikiswano ngeke livote ngalo, licembu letfu kanye nebalingisi betfu labasiphakamisako, labasiphakamisako, nabo abalisekeli.
Ngicela uyekele kufundza i-Chequers bese ulalela.
May watsi: "Baphristi labakhulu bagcina timiso tabo uma bagcina tetsembiso tabo".
Nigel Farage watsi, "Bosopolitiki labatawubakhona kulombhikisho kumele bative bashisa uma ngabe batfola kutsi batfola sincumo lesitsetfwe ku-referendum yanga-2016.
"Manje sekuyindzaba yekwetsemba emkhatsini wetfu nebantfu kanye netiphatsimandla", kwasho yena.
"Benta konkhe lokusemandleni abo kute batsengise nge-Brexit, futsi lamuhla silapha kute sitjele bantfu kutsi ngeke sikwemukele loko.
Akhuluma kulesicumbi lebesikhutsatekile, watsi: "Ngifuna kutsi nine nente bosopolitiki labakhona kutsi bente intsandvo yeBrexit babe nemdlandla.
"Sibutsa emabutfo ebantfu bakulelive lasinikete kuncoba ku-Brexit, futsi angeke siphumle singakabi live lelitimele, lelitimele, lelitigcabhako".
Ngesikhatsi lesifanako, labo lebebangafuni kuphuma kuhulumende wase-UK bahamba baya edolobheni, lapho kwabanjwa khona umbhikisho wema-awa lamabili.
Bantfu labambalwa bebakhutsata emaTory ngekulwa ne-Brexit ngemuva kwekusungulwa kwelicembu ngempelasontfo.
Umshushisi weLabour, Baron Andrew Adonis, wahleka bantfu labambelele kakhulu ku-Tory ngenca yetinkinga tekuphepha ku-app yelicembu lakhe ekucaleni kwalomhlangano.
"Laba bantfu batsi bangakhona kuhlanganisa tinhlelo te-IT nabo bonkhe buchwepheshe kute basite iCanada Plus Plus, umncele lohlantekile, ibhizinisi lelikhululekile ngaphandle kwemincele ne-Ireland", kwengeta yena.
"Loku kuyintfo lengenamsebenti.
Kute intfo lebitwa ngekutsi yi-Brexit lenhle", kwengeta.
Elizabeth Warren uhlose kucabangisisa ngekukhetsa kwakhe kuba ngumengameli
USenator Elizabeth Warren utsi ngemuva kwelukhetfo lwangaNovemba, utawucabanga ngekuncuma kuba ngumengameli.
Ngekusho kwe-Boston Globe, ummeli we-Massachusetts we-Democratic wakhuluma ngelikusasa lakhe emhlanganweni we-Western Massachusetts ngeMgcibelo.
Elizabeth Warren, lohlale agceka Mengameli Donald Trump, utawuncuma kukhetfwa kabusha ngaNovemba, futsi utawuphikisana na Geoff Diehl, umholi we-Republican, lobekaphetse Trump eMassachusetts ngesikhatsi sekukhetfwa kwa-2016.
Lamuhla, kukhona lokukhulunywa ngako kutsi Warren angahle ancobe Trump elukhetfweni lwanga-2020.
Lomcimbi lowabanjwa ngaMgcibelo e Holyoke, bewuyimhlangano wakhe wema-36 nebakhetfwa ehholeni lelidolobha kusukela Donald Trump atsatsa sikhundla.
Lomunye walabo labebakhona wabuta kutsi ngabe uhlele kuba ngumengameli yini.
Elizabeth Warren waphendvula watsi sikhatsi sekutsi bafati baye eWashington kute balungise hulumende wetfu lowonakele, futsi loko kusho kutsi bafati kufanele babe semkhatsini wabo bonkhe labasetulu.
Kuboshwa kwemuntfu lobangele kubulawa kwe-Wayde Sims, umdlali we-LSU
Emaphoyisa aseBaton Rouge, eLouisiana, ngaLesihlanu atsi abambe umuntfu lotsite lobekanesizatfu sekudutjulwa kwebantfu lokwabulala Wayde Sims, lobekangumdlali we-basketball wase-LSU.
Litiko lemaphoyisa laseBaton Rouge litise kutsi libophe Dytone Simpson, loneminyaka lengu-20 budzala, ngesikhatsi semhlangano webantfu lebewubanjwe nga-11:00 ekuseni.
Kulomnyaka, i-video levelako yalomdlalo yakhishwa, yacela lusito lwekwatisa lomuntfu lobonakalako.
Wayde Sims, loneminyaka lengu-20 budzala, wabulawa ngekudutjulwa ngeLesihlanu ekuseni edvute ne-Southern University.
"Wayde Sims udutjwe ngumuntfu lofile ngekudutjwa ngumuntfu lofile", kusho umphatsi wemaphoyisa, Murphy J. Paul, ngekusho kwe-247sports.
Wayde wasita umngani wakhe futsi wabulawa nguSimpson.
Simpson wabutwa ngemibuto, wavuma kutsi bekakhona lapho kwenteka khona lelicala, futsi bekaphetse sibhamu futsi wadubula Wayde.
