Wayde Sims, umfana lonetinyawo letingu-1.98 lowakhulela eBaton Rouge, wadlala imidlalo lengu-32 futsi wacala emahlandla langu-10 emdlalweni wakhe wekugcina, ngesikhatsi achubeka ngekushaya imizuzu lengu-17.4 emdlalweni, akhomba emaphuzu langu-5.6 futsi akhipha 2.9 ngemdlalo.
I-Grand Prix yaseRussia: Lewis Hamilton usondzela ekutfoleni indondo yemhlaba ngemuva kwekunikwa ligunya lekutsi ancobe Sebastian Vettel
Kusukela ngesikhatsi Valtteri Bottas afika ku Lewis Hamilton ngaMgcibelo, kwacaca kutsi kuniketwa kwe Mercedes bekutawuba nemtselela lomkhulu emphumeleni walomncintiswano.
Bottas, lowacala emgceni wekucala, wacala kahle kakhulu futsi wasondzela kuHamilton, wavikela sikhundla sakhe kumgijimi wakhe ngemigca lemibili yekucala waphocelela Vettel kutsi ahlasele umngani wakhe.
Vettel wahamba kucala waya endzaweni yekusebenta futsi wavumela Hamilton kutsi agibele ngemuva kwemahhashi, lokwakungaba ngumphumela wemjaho.
Lomshayeli weMercedes wehla ngemoto emgodleni lolandzelako futsi wafika ngemuva kwaVettel, kepha ngemuva kwekushayisana lokwaholela ekutseni umshayeli weFerrari angafuni kushiya indzawo yangekhatsi, futsi wafuna kuciniswa ngemuva kwekushayisana kwakhe kabili, Hamilton wacala kuhola.
Max Verstappen wacala ngemuva, futsi ngesikhatsi aneminyaka lengu-21 budzala, wafika esigabeni sesikhombisa ekupheleni kwelilayini lekucala.
Ngemuva kwaloko, wahola umjaho lomnyenti ngekutsi angashintji emathayi akhe kute acedze ngekushesha futsi atsatse indzawo yesine kuKimi Raikkonen.
Wagcine ashayela lapho bekabese khona ku-Line 44, kodvwa kwatsi nakufika emalayini lasiphohlongo, wehluleka kuphindze agijime futsi Raikkonen waba sesikhundleni sesine.
"Leli bekulilanga lematima ngobe Valtteri abesebente kahle kakhulu kuleliviki lonkhe futsi bekayindvodza lehloniphekile ngesikhatsi angitjela kutsi angingishiyi.
"Lonkhe licembu letfu belisebenta kamatima kute litfole tindzawo letimbili letisezingeni lelisetulu", kusho Hamilton.
Bekungasiko kukhuluma ngemtimba kahle.
Emhlanganweni lowabanjwa ngeMgcibelo, Mengameli Donald Trump wahleka iSenator Diana Feinstein, lowatsi akazange akhiphe incwadzi yaChristina Blasey Ford, lowamangalela ngelicala lekuhlukunyetwa ngekwelicasi kweMengameli lobekwe nguNkantolo lePhakeme yaseMelika, Brett Kavanaugh.
Akakhulumi ngalokucondzile mayelana nekutfola bufakazi baChristina Ford enkantolo yebucotfo, esikhundleni saloko watsi loko lokwenteka kulelo komiti kukhombisa kutsi bantfu "banelunya, banelunya futsi banemanga".
"Lokwenteka, nguloko, kepha lesimo lesinhle lesisibone kulesigungu lesengamele kulamalanga lambalwa, lapho sibona khona lulaka, lapho sibona khona bantfu labanelulaka, labanelunya, labanelunya, nalabakhohlisako", kwasho yena.
"Sibona loko lokushicilelwe, lokwatiswa, bese batsi, 'Cha, angikenti loko.'
Angikenti loko.
Niyakhumbula yini?
Dianna Feinstein, ngabe uyibhalile yini lendzaba?
Khumbula kutsi waphendvula watsini - ngabe sewutfole loko lokushiwo ngulelikhadi?
Cha, angitsi.
Angizange ngimtjele kutsi ngitsini.
Kulungile, ngivumele ngivule emehlo.
"Cha, asikaze", wengeta, ahlaba umlomo.
Diana Feinstein watfola incwadzi levela kuChristina Ford lechaza simangalo lesimayelana naKavanaugh ngaJulayi, futsi yavela ekucaleni kwaSeptemba.
"Angizange ngivimbele loko lobekushiwo nguDkt. Ford, futsi angizange ngivume kutsi ngivule umlandvo wakhe", kusho Feinstein embikwemkhandlu, njengobe kubikwa kuThe Hill.
"Wangicela kutsi ngihlale ngingakhulumi, futsi ngekulandzela sicelo sakhe, angizange ngivume kutsi loko kubonakale.
Kodvwa lesimemetelo sakhe asizange simente akholwe umengameli, lowatsi emhlanganweni waMgcibelo: "Nginitjela kutsi loko bekungukukhuluma lokungafanele.
Kungenteka kutsi akazange akhulume, kodvwa loko bekungukukhuluma ngemtimba lokwaphitsitela kakhulu lengake ngakubona.
