Linyenti labo libaleka lisuka eChina, lelinelive lelidze kakhulu lelinebuve neNyakatfo Korea, lokwenta kube melula kuwela lelive kunekungena endzaweni levikelwe kakhulu (DMZ) emkhatsini wemaKoreya.
I-China ibuka lababaleki njengebantfu labangenawo emalungelo ebantfu, hhayi njengebantfu lababalekile, futsi ivame kubabuyisela emuva ngenkhani.
Budlelwane emkhatsini weNyakatfo neNingizimu, lobusengotini yekubhekana netimphi, buye batfutfuka kakhulu etinyangeni letimbalwa letengcile.
Kulenyanga, baholi bemave lamabili bahlangana ePyongyang, lapho bacoce khona ngetinkhulumiswano tekucedza kusebentisa i-nuclear, lebekubambelela khona.
Loku kwenteka ngemuva kwekuhlangana lokumangalisako kwe Mengameli waseMelika Donald Trump na Kim Jong Un, lokwenteka eSingapore ngaJuni, lokwaholela esivumelwaneni lesisemtsetfweni sekuhlangana kute kucedvwe tikhali te-nuclear eNhlonhlweni yaseKorea.
Kodvwa ngeMgcibelo, iNdvuna Yetepolitiki yaseNyakatfo Korea, Ri Yong-ho, yatsi iMelika ayenti lutfo ngalendzaba.
"Ngaphandle kwekwetsembela eMelika, kute siciniseko sekuphepha kwetfu, futsi kute nelitfuba lekutsi singenele kucedza tikhali tetfu", kusho Ri endzabeni yakhe lebeyihanjelwe ku-UN General Assembly eNew York.
Nancy Pelosi utsi Brett Kavanaugh 'uyingwadla' futsi akafaneleki kutsi asebente eNkantolo lePhakeme.
Umholi welicembu lelikhulu le-LGBT lobitwa ngekutsi nguNancy Pelosi, utsi Brett Kavanaugh, lotawuba lijaji leNkantolo lePhakeme, "uyingwadla" futsi utsi ngekwemvelo akasiyo iNkantolo lePhakeme.
Pelosi washo lamavi ngesikhatsi ahlanganyela ne-Texas Tribune Festival e-Austin ngaMgcibelo.
"Ngicabanga kutsi kube lomake bekatiphatsa ngalendlela, bekangabitwa ngekutsi 'uyindvodza lenenhlitiyo lembi' " Pelosi watjela umengameli wakhe mayelana nekuphendvula kwakhe ku Kavanaugh ngesikhatsi afakaza kuKhomishane yeTemtsetfo yePhalamende ngeLesine.
Kavanaugh waphika ngekwemivelo kutsi bekangumuntfu lobekahlukubeta Dokotela Christina Blasey Ford ngesikhatsi basakhula.
Ngalesinye sikhatsi ngesikhatsi akhuluma, Kavanaugh abekhombisa luvelo lolukhulu, futsi bekahle amemete aphindze aphelelwe nangemandla ngesikhatsi akhuluma ngemindeni yakhe nangesikhatsi asebusuku esikolweni.
Waphindze wagceka emaDemocrats labekakhona kulelikomidi, watsi usolwa ngekutsi "ngumuntfu lohlukumeta lidumela lakhe" lohlelwe ngema-liberal, labekhatsateke kakhulu ngekulahlekelwa ngu-Hillary Clinton ngumengameli nga-2016.
Pelosi watsi yena utsi emavi aKavanaugh akhombisa kutsi abengakafaneli kuba seNkantolo lePhakeme ngobe aveza kutsi abenenkhani kumaDemocrats.
"Ngicabanga kutsi utivimbele yena ngekwenta letintfo, nangendlela lahlasela ngayo emaClinton nemaDemocrats", kwasho yena.
Ngesikhatsi abuzwa kutsi utawufuna yini kumcosha Kavanaugh esikhundleni uma ngabe abekwa esikhundleni, futsi emaDemocrats atfola linyenti leSigungu, Pelosi watigodla.
"Ngitakusho kutsi nangabe angawakhulumi emaciniso kuKhongolose nobe ku-FBI, angeke nje agcine ngekuhlala eNkantolo lePhakeme, kepha angahle futsi akhonte kuleNkantolo lapho asebenta khona", kwasho yena.
Kavanaugh nyalo sewungumehluleli eNkantolo yeTikhalo ye-District of Columbia.
Pelosi waphindze watsi, njengemDemocrat, wesaba kakhulu kutsi Kavanaugh angahle akhiphe sincumo mayelana neMtsetfo weKunakekela Lokufanelekile nobe Roe v Wade, ngobe yena utsatfwa njengendvuna yelicala lelibukene netekugwema.
Ngesikhatsi sekuciniswa kwelicala lakhe, Kavanaugh akazange abute kutsi ngabe utawugucula yini emacala latsite latsetfwe yiNkantolo lePhakeme.
"Lesi akusiso sikhatsi sekwetfula umuntfu lonenkinga, lonelubandlululo, lofuna kutsi sitsi 'kuhle kakhulu,'" kwasho Pelosi.
Futsi bafati kufanele bawusebentise.
Loku kuyintfo lelungile, tinyanga netinyanga tekutfukutsela, futsi angakhoni kukwehlula ngaphandle kwekukhala.
