Yini lengazuzisa iBeijing emphini yetemnotfo emkhatsini weMelika neChina?
Emagagasi lacala imphi yetemnotfo emkhatsini we US ne China abeyimphumphutse, kantsi nanobe imphi isaphutfuma, kulesikhatsi lesidze, kungcubutana emkhatsini walamave kungasita iBeijing, kusho tati.
Sicwayiso sekucala salomnyaka sentiwa nguMengameli waseMelika Donald Trump, ngekubeka intsela etintfweni letibalulekile letitfunyelwa ngaphandle yiChina, kufaka ekhatsi emaphaneli elanga, insimbi kanye ne-aluminium.
Lokunyenti kwavela kuleliviki ngemuva kwekubekwa kwematselo lamasha etintfo letingu-R200 billion (R130 billion) letingenisa cishe ihhafu yetintfo letingeniswa e-United States tisuka eChina.
Njalo nje, iBeijing iye yabuyisela, muva nje, ngekwenyusa intsela ku-$60 wetigidzigidzi temitfombo yaseMelika, isuka ku-5% iye ku-10%.
I-China itimisele kuphendvula nobe ngabe ngutiphi titsiyo teMelika futsi kubonakala shengatsi umnotfo wesibili emhlabeni wonkhe angeke ushone.
Kuphocelela iWashington kutsi ihambe kusho kutsi iyavumelana netimfuno, kepha kuhlonipha umtsetfo weMelika kuvele kube yintfo leyetfusako ku-Xi Jinping, umengameli wase-China.
Kodvwa, tati titsi nangabe iBeijing idlala kahle, kucindzeteleka lokubangelwa yimphi yekutsengisa neMelika kungenta iChina ibe nemandla esikhatsini lesidze, kunciphise kuncike kwayo kumnotfo webili.
"Lokutsi sincumo lesitsite lesitsatfwe ngekushesha eWashington nobe eBeijing singabangela kutsi kube khona kuhlukunyetwa kwemnotfo kulelinye live, kuyingoti kakhulu kunaloko lokushiwo ngulabanye", kusho Abigail Grace, losati se-Asia ku-Center for New American Security.
INdvuna Yetepolitiki YaseSiriya Yenta Sinyatselo Sekwemukela Babaleki
Hulumende utsi iSyria seyikulungele kwemukela lababaleki ngekutitsandzela, futsi ucela lusito ekwakheni lelive lelichitjwe timphi iminyaka lengetulu kwalesikhombisa.
Ekukhulumeni kwakhe kuMhlangano Wetive Wetive we-UN, Ndvuna Yetepolitiki yase-Syria, Walid al-Moualem, watsi timo kulelive tiyachubeka nekutfutfuka.
"Lesimilo endzaweni yakitsi sesicinile futsi siphephile ngenca yekulwa nekuhlaselwa kwemagciwane", kwasho yena.
Kute kubuyiselwe simo lesivamile, hulumende uyachubeka nekwakha kabusha tindzawo letibhidlitwe ngemaphekula.
Tonkhe timo setihlangene kute kutsi labo lababalekile baphindze babuyele eveni labo ngekutitsandzela, ngenca yekucindzetelwa ngulelive kanye nekuhlaselwa ngetinhlelo tetemnotfo letitsintsa kuphila kwabo kanye netindlela tekutiphilisa.
Ngekusho kwe-UN, bantfu labangetulu kwetigidzi letingu-5.5 bavele eSyria kusukela kwacala lemphi nga-2011.
Labanye bantfu labatigidzi letisitfupha labasaphila lapho badzinga lusito lwetilwembu.
Al-Moualem watsi hulumende waseSiriya utawemukela lusito lwakhe ekwakheni live lelibhidlikile.
Kodvwa waphindze watsi angeke emukele lusito lolunemibandzela nobe loluniketwa ngemave labesekela lemphi.
